{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775855456803,"sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","part":{"id":"prt_d793bce16001iK1UDksXEbAjQD","messageID":"msg_d793bc17200152u5wPytVbUdIY","sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_87d5715d54ae44db917c00a2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-022 — CLI publish 命令\n2: \n3: **Module:** cmd/cli\n4: **Language:** Python\n5: **Size:** L\n6: \n7: ## 目的\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `publish` 子命令，将已构建的 Agent 镜像发布/部署到目标环境。支持两种 provider 模式：`agentcube`（部署 AgentRuntime Custom Resource 到 Kubernetes）和 `k8s`（部署标准 Deployment + NodePort Service）。`publish` 命令负责准备镜像（本地 Docker push 或使用已有 image URL）、创建/更新 Kubernetes 资源、等待部署就绪，并将发布结果持久化回 `agent_metadata.yaml`。\n10: \n11: 当前 Python CLI 已定义 `publish` 命令的 Typer 签名和 `PublishRuntime` 类骨架，但需要完整实现来满足 spec 中定义的行为，包括镜像准备、双 provider 支持、前置校验、部署就绪等待和元数据更新。\n12: \n13: ## 范围\n14: \n15: ### 包含\n16: \n17: 1. **`publish` Typer 命令实现** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n18:    - 所有选项参数：`workspace` (`-f`, 默认 `.`), `version` (`--version`), `image_url` (`--image-url`), `image_username` (`--image-username`), `image_password` (`--image-password`), `description` (`--description`), `region` (`--region`), `cloud_provider` (`--cloud-provider`), `provider` (`--provider`, 默认 `\"agentcube\"`), `node_port` (`--node-port`, `Optional[int]`), `replicas` (`--replicas`), `namespace` (`--namespace`), `verbose` (`--verbose`)\n19:    - 成功输出：Rich 格式显示 provider 类型、部署名称、namespace、endpoint URL\n20:    - 错误处理：通过 `_handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)` 打印红色错误信息，verbose 时打印 traceback，退出码 1\n21:    - Rich `Progress` spinner 在执行期间显示\n22: \n23: 2. **`PublishRuntime` 类完整实现** (`agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`)\n24:    - `publish(workspace_path, **options)` — 主入口，编排完整发布流程\n25:    - `_prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options)` — 根据 build_mode 和 CLI 参数决定镜像来源，返回完整 image tag\n26:    - `_prepare_local_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)` — 本地模式：使用 `DockerService.push_image()` 推送到 registry，需要 `image_url`/`image_username`/`image_password`\n27:    - `_prepare_cloud_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)` — 云端模式：从 metadata 或 CLI 获取已有 image URL\n28:    - `_publish_cr_to_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)` — AgentCube provider：使用 `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime()` 创建/更新 AgentRuntime CR，等待就绪\n29:    - `_publish_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)` — 标准 K8s provider：使用 `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent()` 创建 Deployment + NodePort Service，调用 `wait_for_deployment_ready(..., timeout=120)`\n30:    - `_update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, agent_info)` — 更新 metadata 的 `agent_id`、`agent_endpoint`、`k8s_deployment` 等字段并持久化\n31: \n32: 3. **`AgentCubeProvider` 完整实现** (`agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`)\n33:    - `deploy_agent_runtime(agent_name, image_url, port, entrypoint, env_vars, workload_manager_url, router_url, readiness_probe_path, readiness_probe_port)` — 创建/patch AgentRuntime CR\n34:    - CR API: `group=\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`, `version=\"v1alpha1\"`, `plural=\"agentruntimes\"`\n35:    - 嵌入 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` / `ROUTER_URL` 环境变量（优先参数，fallback 到系统环境变量）\n36:    - 设置 `sessionTimeout: \"15m\"`、`maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"`、`imagePullSecrets: [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]`\n37:    -  readiness probe 配置（当 metadata 中存在 readiness probe 字段时）\n38:    - `_sanitize_name(name)` — 名称合法化\n39:    - `_ensure_namespace()` — 确保 namespace 存在\n40:    - `get_agent_runtime(name, namespace)` — 查询 CR 状态\n41: \n42: 4. **`KubernetesProvider` 完整实现** (`agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`)\n43:    - `deploy_agent(agent_name, image_url, port, entrypoint, replicas, node_port, env_vars)` — 创建 Deployment + NodePort Service\n44:    - `_create_deployment(...)` — 创建或 patch Deployment\n45:    - `_create_service(name, port, node_port)` — 创建 NodePort Service\n46:    - `wait_for_deployment_ready(name, timeout=120)` — 轮询等待 Deployment 就绪，超时抛 `TimeoutError`\n47:    - `get_agent_status(agent_name)` — 查询 Deployment/Service/pod 状态\n48:    - `delete_agent(agent_name)` — 删除 Deployment + Service（忽略 404）\n49:    - `_sanitize_name(name)` — 名称合法化\n50:    - `_ensure_namespace()` — 确保 namespace 存在\n51: \n52: 5. **`StatusRuntime` 状态查询增强** (`agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`)\n53:    - `_get_cr_k8s_status(metadata)` — 读取 AgentRuntime CR 的 `status` 字段，返回 `status`/`agentEndpoint` 或 `created_no_status`/`not_found_in_k8s`\n54: \n55: ### 不包含\n56: \n57: - `pack` / `build` 命令的实现（由 AR-020 / AR-021 覆盖）\n58: - `DockerService.build_image()` 的实现（由 AR-021 覆盖）\n59: - `invoke` 命令的完整实现（依赖 publish 输出的 endpoint，由其他 AR 覆盖）\n60: - Go 二进制入口 (`cmd/agentcube/`, `cmd/agentcube-controller/`) — 独立实现\n61: - CI/CD pipeline 变更\n62: - 云端构建的具体云厂商适配器实现\n63: \n64: ## 架构概要\n65: \n66: ### 组件关系\n67: \n68: ```\n69: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n70: │                    CLI Layer (Typer)                             │\n71: │  agentcube/cli/main.py: publish() command                        │\n72: │  - 解析选项 → 调用 PublishRuntime.publish()                      │\n73: │  - Rich 输出 / _handle_error()                                   │\n74: └──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┘\n75:                            │\n76: ┌──────────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────────┐\n77: │                     Runtime Layer                                │\n78: │  agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py: PublishRuntime            │\n79: │  - 镜像准备 → 前置校验 → 部署 → 元数据更新                       │\n80: │  - 根据 provider 分发到 AgentCubeProvider / KubernetesProvider   │\n81: │  - 依赖 DockerService 推送镜像（本地模式）                       │\n82: │  - 依赖 MetadataService 加载/保存元数据                          │\n83: └───┬──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘\n84:     │                              │\n85: ┌───▼──────────────┐  ┌────────────▼──────────────────────────────┐\n86: │  Service Layer    │  │  Provider Layer                           │\n87: │  DockerService    │  │  ┌─────────────────┐ ┌─────────────────┐  │\n88: │  - push_image     │  │  │ AgentCubeProvider│ │KubernetesProvider│ │\n89: │  - docker_login   │  │  │ - AgentRuntime CR│ │- Deployment     │  │\n90: │  - tag_image      │  │  │ - group: runtime. │ │- NodePort Svc   │  │\n91: │  └───────────────┘  │  │   agentcube...   │ │- wait_for_ready │  │\n92:                       │  └─────────────────┘ └─────────────────┘  │\n93:                       └───────────────────────────────────────────┘\n94: ```\n95: \n96: ### 发布流程\n97: \n98: ```\n99: publish() CLI\n100:   │\n101:   ├── PublishRuntime.publish()\n102:   │     │\n103:   │     ├── 1. 加载 agent_metadata.yaml\n104:   │     │\n105:   │     ├── 2. 合并 CLI 选项到 metadata（version, description, region 等）\n106:   │     │\n107:   │     ├── 3. _prepare_image_for_publishing()\n108:   │     │     ├── build_mode == \"local\" → _prepare_local_image()\n109:   │     │     │     └── DockerService.push_image(registry_url, username, password)\n110:   │     │     └── build_mode == \"cloud\" → _prepare_cloud_image()\n111:   │     │           └── 使用已有 image URL（从 metadata 或 CLI --image-url）\n112:   │     │\n113:   │     ├── 4. 根据 provider 分发\n114:   │     │     ├── \"agentcube\" → _publish_cr_to_k8s()\n115:   │     │     │     ├── 校验 router_url 和 workload_manager_url\n116:   │     │     │     └── AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime()\n117:   │     │     │           └── 创建/patch AgentRuntime CR\n118:   │     │     └── \"k8s\" → _publish_k8s()\n119:   │     │           ├── KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent()\n120:   │     │           │     ├── _create_deployment()\n121:   │     │           │     └── _create_service()\n122:   │     │           └── wait_for_deployment_ready(timeout=120)\n123:   │     │\n124:   │     ├── 5. _update_publish_metadata()\n125:   │     │     └── 保存 agent_id, agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment\n126:   │     │\n127:   │     └── 6. 返回部署结果\n128:   │\n129:   └── CLI 输出: provider, deployment_name, namespace, endpoint\n130: ```\n131: \n132: ### 目录结构（新增/修改的文件）\n133: \n134: ```\n135: cmd/cli/\n136: ├── agentcube/\n137: │   ├── cli/\n138: │   │   └── main.py                    # 修改: 实现 publish() 命令体\n139: │   ├── runtime/\n140: │   │   └── publish_runtime.py         # 实现: PublishRuntime 类\n141: │   └── services/\n142: │       ├── agentcube_provider.py      # 实现: AgentCubeProvider 类\n143: │       └── k8s_provider.py            # 实现: KubernetesProvider 类\n144: ```\n145: \n146: ## 影响分析\n147: \n148: ### 直接影响\n149: \n150: | 文件 | 变更类型 | 说明 |\n151: |------|----------|------|\n152: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | 修改 | 实现 `publish()` 命令体，调用 `PublishRuntime` |\n153: | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | 实现 | 完整实现所有方法 |\n154: | `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | 实现 | AgentRuntime CR 的创建/patch/查询 |\n155: | `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | 实现 | Deployment/Service 的创建/等待就绪/查询/删除 |\n156: | `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | 确认 | 确保 `push_image` 支持 publish 场景 |\n157: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | 确认 | 确保 load/save 支持 publish 元数据字段 |\n158: | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | 确认 | `_get_cr_k8s_status` 依赖 publish 输出的 CR |\n159: \n160: ### 上游依赖（本变更依赖的已完成组件）\n161: \n162: - **AR-020 (`pack` 命令)** — 依赖 pack 生成的 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n163: - **AR-021 (`build` 命令)** — 依赖 build 产出的容器镜像和更新后的 metadata.image\n164: - `typer[all]>=0.9.0` — CLI 框架（已有依赖）\n165: - `pydantic>=2.0.0` — 元数据验证（已有依赖）\n166: - `pyyaml>=6.0` — YAML 序列化（已有依赖）\n167: - `docker>=6.0.0` — Docker SDK for Python（已有依赖，本地 push 模式）\n168: - `rich>=13.0.0` — Progress spinner、Table 格式化输出（已有依赖）\n169: - `kubernetes>=28.0.0` — Kubernetes Python client（optional 依赖，publish/invoke/status 需要）\n170: - `httpx>=0.24.0` — HTTP 客户端（已有依赖）\n171: \n172: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n173: \n174: - **AR: `invoke` 命令** — 依赖 publish 部署后的 agent endpoint 进行调用\n175: - **AR: `status` 命令** — 依赖 publish 输出的 metadata 展示部署状态\n176: \n177: ### 无影响的组件\n178: \n179: - `PackRuntime` / `BuildRuntime` — 本 AR 不修改 pack/build 逻辑\n180: - `InvokeRuntime` / `StatusRuntime` 的核心方法 — 仅确认现有接口兼容\n181: - Go 二进制入口 (`cmd/agentcube/`, `cmd/agentcube-controller/`) — 独立实现\n182: - Python SDK (`sdk-python/`) — 独立实现\n183: \n184: ### 风险评估\n185: \n186: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n187: |------|------|----------|\n188: | Kubernetes 集群不可达或 kubeconfig 配置错误 | 高 | `_ensure_namespace()` 提前验证连接，给出清晰的错误提示 |\n189: | AgentRuntime CR 部署后长时间未就绪 | 高 | 设置合理的超时等待（参考 K8s provider 的 120s timeout），超时后记录错误到 metadata |\n190: | 本地镜像推送失败（registry 认证/网络） | 高 | `_prepare_local_image` 中先执行 `DockerService._docker_login_sdk`，失败时给出明确指引 |\n191: | `router_url` 或 `workload_manager_url` 缺失导致 AgentCube 部署失败 | 中 | 前置校验在 `_publish_cr_to_k8s` 中检查，抛出 `ValueError` 要求配置 |\n192: | `node_port` 冲突（30000-32767 范围） | 中 | K8s 会拒绝冲突的 NodePort，捕获异常并提示用户更换 |\n193: | 镜像拉取失败（imagePullSecrets 配置不正确） | 中 | CR 中使用 `default-secret`，用户需提前配置；部署失败后通过 status 命令诊断 |\n194: | namespace 不存在导致部署失败 | 低 | `_ensure_namespace()` 自动创建 namespace |\n195: \n196: ## 备选方案\n197: \n198: ### 1. PublishRuntime 类编排所有发布步骤（✅ 选定方案）\n199: \n200: **做法**：`PublishRuntime` 类包含所有私有方法，在 `publish()` 中顺序调用，与 `PackRuntime` / `BuildRuntime` 模式一致。\n201: \n202: **优点**：\n203: - 与现有 `PackRuntime` / `BuildRuntime` 架构一致，降低认知负担\n204: - 逻辑集中，易于调试和测试\n205: - 与 spec 中定义的类结构完全匹配\n206: \n207: **缺点**：\n208: - 类包含多种职责（镜像准备、部署、元数据更新）\n209: - AgentCube CR 和标准 K8s 部署逻辑差异较大\n210: \n211: **决策**：采用。与现有 spec 和架构一致，通过 provider 参数分发到不同的 Provider 类，保持职责分离。\n212: \n213: ### 2. 部署策略模式分离 AgentCube / K8s\n214: \n215: **做法**：定义 `DeployStrategy` 接口，`AgentCubeDeployStrategy` 和 `K8sDeployStrategy` 实现，`PublishRuntime` 委托给策略。\n216: \n217: **优点**：\n218: - 两种部署逻辑完全隔离\n219: - 添加新 provider（如 AWS ECS、GCP Cloud Run）只需新策略\n220: \n221: **缺点**：\n222: - 增加抽象层，对当前仅 2 种 provider 来说过度设计\n223: - 与 spec 中定义的 `_publish_cr_to_k8s` / `_publish_k8s` 私有方法结构不一致\n224: \n225: **决策**：不采用。当前仅支持 agentcube/k8s，策略模式增加复杂度。Provider 层已通过 `AgentCubeProvider` / `KubernetesProvider` 实现职责分离。可在未来添加第 3 种 provider 时重构。\n226: \n227: ### 3. 镜像准备与部署分离为两个命令\n228: \n229: **做法**：将 `publish` 拆分为 `push`（仅推送镜像）和 `deploy`（仅部署资源）两个命令。\n230: \n231: **优点**：\n232: - 职责更清晰，用户可以单独推送镜像或单独部署\n233: - 支持跨环境复用同一镜像（push 一次，deploy 多次）\n234: \n235: **缺点**：\n236: - 与 spec 中单一 `publish` 命令的设计不符\n237: - 增加用户学习成本（需要理解两个命令的关系）\n238: - 当前用户场景是\"一次发布完成所有步骤\"\n239: \n240: **决策**：不采用。遵循 spec 中 `publish` 命令的单一入口设计。内部通过 `_prepare_image_for_publishing` 和 `_publish_cr_to_k8s` / `_publish_k8s` 实现逻辑分离。\n241: \n242: ## 实现要点\n243: \n244: ### `publish` 命令流程\n245: \n246: ```python\n247: @app.command()\n248: def publish(\n249:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", ...),\n250:     version: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--version\", ...),\n251:     image_url: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-url\", ...),\n252:     image_username: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-username\", ...),\n253:     image_password: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-password\", ...),\n254:     description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--description\", ...),\n255:     region: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--region\", ...),\n256:     cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\", ...),\n257:     provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\", ...),\n258:     node_port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--node-port\", ...),\n259:     replicas: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--replicas\", ...),\n260:     namespace: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--namespace\", ...),\n261:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", ...),\n262: ) -> None:\n263:     workspace_path = Path(workspace).resolve()\n264:     try:\n265:         with Progress() as progress:\n266:             task = progress.add_task(\"Publishing...\", total=None)\n267:             runtime = PublishRuntime(verbose=verbose, provider=provider)\n268:             result = runtime.publish(\n269:                 workspace_path,\n270:                 version=version,\n271:                 image_url=image_url,\n272:                 image_username=image_username,\n273:                 image_password=image_password,\n274:                 description=description,\n275:                 region=region,\n276:                 cloud_provider=cloud_provider,\n277:                 node_port=node_port,\n278:                 replicas=replicas,\n279:                 namespace=namespace,\n280:             )\n281:         # Rich 输出: provider, deployment_name, namespace, endpoint\n282:     except Exception as e:\n283:         _handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)\n284: ```\n285: \n286: ### `PublishRuntime.publish()` 内部流程\n287: \n288: ```python\n289: def publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n290:     # 1. 加载元数据\n291:     metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n292: \n293:     # 2. 合并 CLI 选项\n294:     if options.get(\"version\"):\n295:         metadata.version = options[\"version\"]\n296:     if options.get(\"description\"):\n297:         metadata.description = options[\"description\"]\n298:     if options.get(\"region\"):\n299:         metadata.region = options[\"region\"]\n300:     if options.get(\"namespace\"):\n301:         self.namespace = options[\"namespace\"]\n302: \n303:     # 3. 准备镜像\n304:     image_tag = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n305: \n306:     # 4. 根据 provider 分发\n307:     if self.provider == \"agentcube\":\n308:         agent_info = self._publish_cr_to_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\n309:     else:\n310:         agent_info = self._publish_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\n311: \n312:     # 5. 更新元数据\n313:     self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, agent_info)\n314: \n315:     return agent_info\n316: ```\n317: \n318: ### 镜像准备 — 本地模式\n319: \n320: ```python\n321: def _prepare_local_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str:\n322:     docker_service = DockerService(verbose=self.verbose)\n323: \n324:     registry_url = options.get(\"image_url\") or metadata.registry_url or metadata.image.get(\"name\")\n325:     username = options.get(\"image_username\") or metadata.registry_username\n326:     password = options.get(\"image_password\") or metadata.registry_password\n327: \n328:     if not registry_url:\n329:         raise ValueError(\"--image-url is required in local build mode\")\n330: \n331:     tag = metadata.version or \"latest\"\n332:     source_image = f\"{metadata.image.get('name', metadata.agent_name)}:{tag}\"\n333: \n334:     # 推送镜像\n335:     push_result = docker_service.push_image(\n336:         image_name=source_image,\n337:         registry_url=registry_url,\n338:         username=username,\n339:         password=password,\n340:     )\n341: \n342:     return push_result[\"pushed_image\"]\n343: ```\n344: \n345: ### 镜像准备 — 云端模式\n346: \n347: ```python\n348: def _prepare_cloud_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str:\n349:     image_url = options.get(\"image_url\")\n350:     if image_url:\n351:         return image_url\n352: \n353:     if metadata.image and metadata.image.get(\"name\"):\n354:         tag = metadata.version or \"latest\"\n355:         return f\"{metadata.image['name']}:{tag}\"\n356: \n357:     raise ValueError(\"Image URL not found. Specify --image-url or ensure metadata.image is set.\")\n358: ```\n359: \n360: ### AgentCube CR 部署\n361: \n362: ```python\n363: def _publish_cr_to_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n364:     # 前置校验\n365:     if not metadata.router_url:\n366:         raise ValueError(\n367:             \"router_url is required for AgentCube provider. \"\n368:             \"Set it in agent_metadata.yaml or via CLI options.\"\n369:         )\n370:     if not metadata.workload_manager_url:\n371:         raise ValueError(\n372:             \"workload_manager_url is required for AgentCube provider. \"\n373:             \"Set it in agent_metadata.yaml or via CLI options.\"\n374:         )\n375: \n376:     provider = AgentCubeProvider(\n377:         namespace=self.namespace,\n378:         verbose=self.verbose,\n379:     )\n380: \n381:     result = provider.deploy_agent_runtime(\n382:         agent_name=metadata.agent_name,\n383:         image_url=self._prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options),\n384:         port=metadata.port,\n385:         entrypoint=metadata.entrypoint,\n386:         env_vars=None,\n387:         workload_manager_url=metadata.workload_manager_url,\n388:         router_url=metadata.router_url,\n389:         readiness_probe_path=metadata.readiness_probe_path,\n390:         readiness_probe_port=metadata.readiness_probe_port,\n391:     )\n392: \n393:     return {\n394:         \"provider\": \"agentcube\",\n395:         \"agent_name\": metadata.agent_name,\n396:         \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n397:         \"cr_name\": result.get(\"cr_name\", metadata.agent_name),\n398:         \"status\": result.get(\"status\", \"created\"),\n399:     }\n400: ```\n401: \n402: ### 标准 K8s 部署\n403: \n404: ```python\n405: def _publish_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n406:     provider = KubernetesProvider(\n407:         namespace=self.namespace,\n408:         verbose=self.verbose,\n409:     )\n410: \n411:     image_tag = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n412:     replicas = options.get(\"replicas\") or 1\n413:     node_port = options.get(\"node_port\")\n414: \n415:     result = provider.deploy_agent(\n416:         agent_name=metadata.agent_name,\n417:         image_url=image_tag,\n418:         port=metadata.port,\n419:         entrypoint=metadata.entrypoint,\n420:         replicas=replicas,\n421:         node_port=node_port,\n422:         env_vars=None,\n423:     )\n424: \n425:     # 等待部署就绪\n426:     try:\n427:         provider.wait_for_deployment_ready(result[\"deployment_name\"], timeout=120)\n428:         result[\"status\"] = \"ready\"\n429:     except TimeoutError:\n430:         result[\"status\"] = \"error\"\n431:         result[\"error\"] = \"Deployment did not become ready within 120 seconds\"\n432:         # 记录错误到 metadata\n433:         metadata.k8s_deployment = result\n434:         self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n435:         raise RuntimeError(result[\"error\"])\n436: \n437:     return result\n438: ```\n439: \n440: ### `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime()` 关键实现\n441: \n442: ```python\n443: def deploy_agent_runtime(\n444:     self, agent_name, image_url, port, entrypoint=None,\n445:     env_vars=None, workload_manager_url=None, router_url=None,\n446:     readiness_probe_path=None, readiness_probe_port=None,\n447: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n448:     self._ensure_namespace()\n449:     sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n450: \n451:     # 构建 CR 对象\n452:     cr_body = {\n453:         \"apiVersion\": \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\",\n454:         \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n455:         \"metadata\": {\"name\": sanitized_name, \"namespace\": self.namespace},\n456:         \"spec\": {\n457:             \"image\": image_url,\n458:             \"port\": port,\n459:             \"sessionTimeout\": \"15m\",\n460:             \"maxSessionDuration\": \"8h\",\n461:             \"imagePullSecrets\": [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}],\n462:             \"env\": [],\n463:         },\n464:     }\n465: \n466:     # 环境变量\n467:     env_list = list(env_vars.items()) if env_vars else []\n468:     wm_url = workload_manager_url or os.environ.get(\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\", \"\")\n469:     r_url = router_url or os.environ.get(\"ROUTER_URL\", \"\")\n470:     if wm_url:\n471:         env_list.append({\"name\": \"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\", \"value\": wm_url})\n472:     if r_url:\n473:         env_list.append({\"name\": \"ROUTER_URL\", \"value\": r_url})\n474:     if env_list:\n475:         cr_body[\"spec\"][\"env\"] = env_list\n476: \n477:     # Readiness probe\n478:     if readiness_probe_path and readiness_probe_port:\n479:         cr_body[\"spec\"][\"readinessProbe\"] = {\n480:             \"httpGet\": {\"path\": readiness_probe_path, \"port\": readiness_probe_port},\n481:         }\n482: \n483:     # 创建或 patch\n484:     try:\n485:         existing = self.get_agent_runtime(sanitized_name, self.namespace)\n486:         if existing:\n487:             # Patch\n488:             self.custom_objects.patch_namespaced_custom_object(\n489:                 group=\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n490:                 version=\"v1alpha1\",\n491:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n492:                 plural=\"agentruntimes\",\n493:                 name=sanitized_name,\n494:                 body=cr_body,\n495:             )\n496:         else:\n497:             self.custom_objects.create_namespaced_custom_object(\n498:                 group=\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n499:                 version=\"v1alpha1\",\n500:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n501:                 plural=\"agentruntimes\",\n502:                 body=cr_body,\n503:             )\n504:     except Exception as e:\n505:         raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to deploy AgentRuntime CR: {e}\")\n506: \n507:     return {\"cr_name\": sanitized_name, \"namespace\": self.namespace, \"status\": \"created\"}\n508: ```\n509: \n510: ### `KubernetesProvider.wait_for_deployment_ready()` 实现\n511: \n512: ```python\n513: def wait_for_deployment_ready(self, name: str, timeout: int = 120) -> None:\n514:     start = time.time()\n515:     while time.time() - start < timeout:\n516:         try:\n517:             deployment = self.apps_v1.read_namespaced_deployment(name, self.namespace)\n518:             if (\n519:                 deployment.status.ready_replicas\n520:                 and deployment.status.ready_replicas == deployment.spec.replicas\n521:             ):\n522:                 return\n523:         except ApiException:\n524:             pass\n525:         time.sleep(2)\n526:     raise TimeoutError(\n527:         f\"Deployment {name} did not become ready within {timeout} seconds\"\n528:     )\n529: ```\n530: \n531: ### `_update_publish_metadata()` 实现\n532: \n533: ```python\n534: def _update_publish_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, agent_info: Dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n535:     metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n536: \n537:     metadata.agent_id = agent_info.get(\"agent_name\") or agent_info.get(\"deployment_name\")\n538:     metadata.k8s_deployment = {\n539:         \"type\": \"AgentRuntime\" if agent_info.get(\"provider\") == \"agentcube\" else \"Deployment\",\n540:         \"name\": agent_info.get(\"cr_name\") or agent_info.get(\"deployment_name\"),\n541:         \"namespace\": agent_info.get(\"namespace\"),\n542:     }\n543: \n544:     # 构建 endpoint URL\n545:     if agent_info.get(\"provider\") == \"k8s\" and agent_info.get(\"service_url\"):\n546:         metadata.agent_endpoint = agent_info[\"service_url\"]\n547:     elif agent_info.get(\"provider\") == \"agentcube\":\n548:         # CR 部署后 endpoint 由 Router 提供，初始为占位\n549:         metadata.agent_endpoint = None\n550: \n551:     self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n552: ```\n553: \n554: ## 验收标准\n555: \n556: - [ ] `publish` 命令接受所有指定选项，使用正确默认值\n557: - [ ] `workspace` 默认 `.`，可通过 `-f` / `--workspace` 覆盖\n558: - [ ] `provider` 默认 `\"agentcube\"`，可通过 `--provider` 切换为 `\"k8s\"`\n559: - [ ] AgentCube provider：metadata 缺少 `router_url` 或 `workload_manager_url` 时抛出 `ValueError`\n560: - [ ] AgentCube provider：创建/patch AgentRuntime CR 到 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/agentruntimes`\n561: - [ ] AgentCube provider：CR 包含 `sessionTimeout: \"15m\"`、`maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"`、`imagePullSecrets`\n562: - [ ] AgentCube provider：环境变量嵌入 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` / `ROUTER_URL`（参数优先，fallback 到环境变量）\n563: - [ ] K8s provider：创建 Deployment + NodePort Service\n564: - [ ] K8s provider：调用 `wait_for_deployment_ready(..., timeout=120)`，超时抛 `RuntimeError`\n565: - [ ] K8s provider：`--replicas` 控制副本数，`--node-port` 指定 NodePort（30000-32767）\n566: - [ ] K8s provider：`--namespace` 控制部署 namespace\n567: - [ ] 本地 build 模式：`--image-url` 为必需参数，使用 `DockerService.push_image()` 推送\n568: - [ ] 云端 build 模式：使用已有 image URL（metadata 或 `--image-url`）\n569: - [ ] 发布成功后更新 `metadata.agent_id`、`metadata.agent_endpoint`、`metadata.k8s_deployment`\n570: - [ ] 发布失败时记录错误到 metadata 并抛出异常\n571: - [ ] 成功消息显示 provider 类型、部署名称、namespace、endpoint（Rich 格式）\n572: - [ ] 错误处理打印红色消息 + traceback（verbose），退出码 1\n573: - [ ] Rich `Progress` spinner 在执行期间显示\n574: - [ ] `--verbose` 启用详细日志输出\n575: - [ ] `--version` 选项覆盖 metadata 中的版本号\n576: - [ ] `--description` 和 `--region` 选项更新 metadata 对应字段\n577: - [ ] `status` 命令能正确读取 AgentRuntime CR 的 status 字段\n578: \n579: ## 状态\n580: \n581: - [ ] 提案审查\n582: - [ ] 实现\n583: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 583 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli\n**Language:** Python\n**Size:** L\n\n## 目的\n\n为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `publish` 子命令，将已构建的 Agent 镜像发布/部署到目标环境。支持两种 provider 模式：`agentcube`（部署 AgentRuntime Custom Resource 到 Kubernetes）和 `k8s`（部署标准 Deployment + NodePort Service）。`publish` 命令负责准备镜像（本地 Docker push 或使用已有 image URL）、创建/更新 Kubernetes 资源、等待部署就绪，并将发布结果持久化回 `agent_metadata.yaml`。\n\n当前 Python CLI 已定义 `publish` 命令的 Typer 签名和 `PublishRuntime` 类骨架，但需要完整实现来满足 spec 中定义的行为，包括镜像准备、双 provider 支持、前置校验、部署就绪等待和元数据更新。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n\n1. **`publish` Typer 命令实现** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n   - 所有选项参数：`workspace` (`-f`, 默认 `.`), `version` (`--version`), `image_url` (`--image-url`), `image_username` (`--image-username`), `image_password` (`--image-password`), `description` (`--description`), `region` (`--region`), `cloud_provider` (`--cloud-provider`), `provider` (`--provider`, 默认 `\"agentcube\"`), `node_port` (`--node-port`, `Optional[int]`), `replicas` (`--replicas`), `namespace` (`--namespace`), `verbose` (`--verbose`)\n   - 成功输出：Rich 格式显示 provider 类型、部署名称、namespace、endpoint URL\n   - 错误处理：通过 `_handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)` 打印红色错误信息，verbose 时打印 traceback，退出码 1","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775855456786,"end":1775855456800}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775855458020,"sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","part":{"id":"prt_d793bd29500141UdFNmSg1iFpp","messageID":"msg_d793bc17200152u5wPytVbUdIY","sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_534eacdcc33147aaa80dd70e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 — Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: The `publish` command deploys a packaged and built agent to a target Kubernetes cluster. It supports two providers:\n6: - **`agentcube`** (default): Deploys an AgentRuntime Custom Resource (CR) to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n7: - **`k8s`**: Deploys standard Kubernetes Deployment + NodePort Service\n8: \n9: The command handles image preparation (local Docker push or cloud image URL), provider-specific deployment, metadata updates, and readiness verification. It is the third step in the agent lifecycle pipeline: `pack → build → publish → invoke`.\n10: \n11: ## Architecture\n12: \n13: ### 2.1 Data Flow\n14: \n15: ```\n16: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n17: │                          CLI (Typer)                                  │\n18: │   kubectl-agentcube publish -f <workspace> [--provider agentcube]    │\n19: └────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n20:                          │ options dict\n21:                          ▼\n22: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n23: │                       PublishRuntime                                  │\n24: │  ┌──────────────────┬──────────────────┬──────────────────────────┐  │\n25: │  │ _prepare_image_  │ _publish_cr_to_  │ _publish_k8s             │  │\n26: │  │ for_publishing   │ k8s              │                          │  │\n27: │  └────────┬─────────┴────────┬─────────┴────────────┬─────────────┘  │\n28: │           │                  │                      │                 │\n29: │           ▼                  ▼                      ▼                 │\n30: │  ┌────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐   │\n31: │  │ _prepare_local │  │ AgentCubeProvider│  │ KubernetesProvider │   │\n32: │  │ _image         │  │ .deploy_agent_   │  │ .deploy_agent()    │   │\n33: │  │ _prepare_cloud │  │ runtime()        │  │ .wait_for_deploy   │   │\n34: │  │ _image         │  │                  │  │ ment_ready()       │   │\n35: │  └────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘  └────────────────────┘   │\n36: │                                                                      │\n37: │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n38: │  │ _update_publish_metadata() → agent_metadata.yaml               │  │\n39: │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n40: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n41:                          │\n42:                          ▼\n43: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n44: │                    Rich Output                                        │\n45: │  \"✓ Agent published successfully\"                                    │\n46: │    Agent: <name>  Provider: <provider>  Endpoint: <url>              │\n47: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n48: ```\n49: \n50: ### 2.2 Package Layout (publish-relevant modules)\n51: \n52: ```\n53: cmd/cli/\n54: ├── pyproject.toml                     — Dependencies, console script entry\n55: ├── agentcube/\n56: │   ├── __init__.py                    — __version__, PublishRuntime export\n57: │   ├── cli/\n58: │   │   ├── __init__.py                — Subpackage marker\n59: │   │   └── main.py                    — Typer app, publish() command, _handle_error\n60: │   ├── models/\n61: │   │   └── pack_models.py             — MetadataOptions dataclass\n62: │   ├── runtime/\n63: │   │   ├── __init__.py                — Re-exports PublishRuntime\n64: │   │   └── publish_runtime.py         — PublishRuntime class\n65: │   └── services/\n66: │       ├── __init__.py                — Services package docstring\n67: │       ├── metadata_service.py         — AgentMetadata, MetadataService\n68: │       ├── docker_service.py           — DockerService (image push)\n69: │       ├── k8s_provider.py             — KubernetesProvider (Deployment + Service)\n70: │       └── agentcube_provider.py       — AgentCubeProvider (AgentRuntime CR)\n71: └── examples/\n72:     ├── hello-agent/main.py            — Example Python agent\n73:     └── math-agent/main.py             — Example Python agent\n74: ```\n75: \n76: ### 2.3 Dependencies\n77: \n78: | Module | Purpose |\n79: |--------|---------|\n80: | `typer[all]>=0.9.0` | CLI framework, Rich markup |\n81: | `pydantic>=2.0.0` | AgentMetadata validation |\n82: | `pyyaml>=6.0` | YAML load/dump for agent_metadata.yaml |\n83: | `docker>=6.0.0` | Docker SDK for image push (local mode) |\n84: | `kubernetes>=28.0.0` | K8s client library (optional, for K8s provider) |\n85: | `rich>=13.0.0` | Progress spinner, colored output, tables |\n86: | `httpx>=0.24.0` | HTTP client (indirect, used by providers) |\n87: \n88: ---\n89: \n90: ## Component Design\n91: \n92: ### 3.1 PublishRuntime (`agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`)\n93: \n94: ```python\n95: class PublishRuntime:\n96:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None: ...\n97:     def publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n98:     def _publish_cr_to_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n99:     def _publish_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n100:     def _prepare_image_for_publishing(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str: ...\n101:     def _prepare_local_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str: ...\n102:     def _prepare_cloud_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str: ...\n103:     def _update_publish_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, agent_info: Dict[str, Any]) -> None: ...\n104: ```\n105: \n106: ### 3.2 CLI Command Signature\n107: \n108: ```\n109: kubectl-agentcube publish [OPTIONS]\n110: ```\n111: \n112: | Option | Short | Type | Default | Description |\n113: |--------|-------|------|---------|-------------|\n114: | `--workspace` | `-f` | `str` | `\".\"` | Path to the agent workspace directory |\n115: | `--version` | — | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Semantic version string (e.g., v1.0.0) |\n116: | `--image-url` | — | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Image repository URL (required in local build mode) |\n117: | `--image-username` | — | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Username for image repository |\n118: | `--image-password` | — | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Password for image repository |\n119: | `--description` | — | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Agent description |\n120: | `--region` | — | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Deployment region |\n121: | `--cloud-provider` | — | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Cloud provider name (e.g., huawei) |\n122: | `--provider` | — | `str` | `\"agentcube\"` | Target provider: `agentcube` (AgentRuntime CR) or `k8s` (Deployment/Service) |\n123: | `--node-port` | — | `Optional[int]` | `None` | Specific NodePort (30000-32767) for K8s deployment |\n124: | `--replicas` | — | `Optional[int]` | `None` | Number of replicas for K8s deployment (default: 1) |\n125: | `--namespace` | — | `Optional[str]` | `None` | The namespace for the deployment |\n126: | `--verbose` | — | `bool` | `False` | Enable detailed logging |\n127: \n128: ### 3.3 Sentinel Errors\n129: \n130: ```python\n131: # PublishRuntime\n132: ValueError(\"Workspace directory does not exist: {path}\")\n133: ValueError(\"Image URL is required for local build mode\")\n134: ValueError(\"router_url and workload_manager_url are required in agent_metadata.yaml for AgentCube provider\")\n135: ValueError(\"NodePort must be between 30000 and 32767\")\n136: RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n137: RuntimeError(\"Deployment {name} did not become ready within {timeout}s\")\n138: ```\n139: \n140: ---\n141: \n142: ## Data Flow\n143: \n144: ### 4.1 publish() Main Orchestration\n145: \n146: ```python\n147: def publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n148:     # 1. Validate workspace path\n149:     if not workspace_path.exists():\n150:         raise ValueError(f\"Workspace directory does not exist: {workspace_path}\")\n151:     if not workspace_path.is_dir():\n152:         raise ValueError(f\"Workspace path is not a directory: {workspace_path}\")\n153: \n154:     # 2. Load metadata\n155:     service = MetadataService(verbose=self.verbose)\n156:     metadata = service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n157: \n158:     # 3. Apply CLI option overrides\n159:     for key in [\"version\", \"description\", \"region\"]:\n160:         value = options.get(key)\n161:         if value is not None:\n162:             setattr(metadata, key, value)\n163: \n164:     # 4. Validate node_port range if provided\n165:     node_port = options.get(\"node_port\")\n166:     if node_port is not None and not (30000 <= node_port <= 32767):\n167:         raise ValueError(\"NodePort must be between 30000 and 32767\")\n168: \n169:     # 5. Prepare image for publishing\n170:     image_url = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n171: \n172:     # 6. Route to provider-specific publish\n173:     if self.provider == \"agentcube\":\n174:         result = self._publish_cr_to_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, image_url=image_url, **options)\n175:     elif self.provider == \"k8s\":\n176:         result = self._publish_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, image_url=image_url, **options)\n177:     else:\n178:         raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported provider: {self.provider}\")\n179: \n180:     # 7. Update metadata with deployment info\n181:     self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, result)\n182: \n183:     return result\n184: ```\n185: \n186: ### 4.2 Image Preparation Flow\n187: \n188: ```\n189: _prepare_image_for_publishing()\n190:          │\n191:          ├── metadata.build_mode == \"local\"\n192:          │        │\n193:          │        ├── image_url from CLI required\n194:          │        │\n195:          │        └── _prepare_local_image()\n196:          │                 │\n197:          │                 ├── DockerService.check_docker_available()\n198:          │                 ├── DockerService._docker_login_sdk() (if credentials)\n199:          │                 └── DockerService.push_image()\n200:          │\n201:          └── metadata.build_mode == \"cloud\"\n202:                   │\n203:                   └── _prepare_cloud_image()\n204:                            │\n205:                            └── Resolve cloud image URL from metadata/options\n206: ```\n207: \n208: ### 4.3 _prepare_image_for_publishing\n209: \n210: ```python\n211: def _prepare_image_for_publishing(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str:\n212:     if metadata.build_mode == \"local\":\n213:         return self._prepare_local_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n214:     elif metadata.build_mode == \"cloud\":\n215:         return self._prepare_cloud_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n216:     else:\n217:         raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported build mode: {metadata.build_mode}\")\n218: ```\n219: \n220: ### 4.4 _prepare_local_image\n221: \n222: ```python\n223: def _prepare_local_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str:\n224:     docker_service = DockerService(verbose=self.verbose)\n225: \n226:     if not docker_service.check_docker_available():\n227:         raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n228: \n229:     image_url = options.get(\"image_url\")\n230:     if not image_url:\n231:         raise ValueError(\"Image URL is required for local build mode\")\n232: \n233:     # Build image tag\n234:     version = metadata.version or \"latest\"\n235:     image_tag = f\"{image_url}:{version}\"\n236: \n237:     # Login if credentials provided\n238:     username = options.get(\"image_username\") or metadata.registry_username\n239:     password = options.get(\"image_password\") or metadata.registry_password\n240:     registry_url = options.get(\"registry_url\") or metadata.registry_url\n241: \n242:     if username and password:\n243:         docker_service._docker_login_sdk(registry_url, username, password)\n244: \n245:     # Push image\n246:     result = docker_service.push_image(image_tag, registry_url, username, password)\n247:     return result.get(\"pushed_image\", image_tag)\n248: ```\n249: \n250: ### 4.5 _prepare_cloud_image\n251: \n252: ```python\n253: def _prepare_cloud_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str:\n254:     # Cloud build mode: image already built in cloud, resolve URL\n255:     image_url = options.get(\"image_url\")\n256:     if image_url:\n257:         return image_url\n258: \n259:     if metadata.image and metadata.image.get(\"url\"):\n260:         return metadata.image[\"url\"]\n261: \n262:     raise ValueError(\"Image URL is required for cloud build mode\")\n263: ```\n264: \n265: ### 4.6 AgentCube Provider Flow (_publish_cr_to_k8s)\n266: \n267: ```python\n268: def _publish_cr_to_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n269:     # Validate prerequisites\n270:     if not metadata.router_url:\n271:         raise ValueError(\"router_url and workload_manager_url are required in agent_metadata.yaml for AgentCube provider\")\n272:     if not metadata.workload_manager_url:\n273:         raise ValueError(\"router_url and workload_manager_url are required in agent_metadata.yaml for AgentCube provider\")\n274: \n275:     # Initialize provider\n276:     namespace = options.get(\"namespace\") or \"default\"\n277:     provider = AgentCubeProvider(namespace=namespace, verbose=self.verbose)\n278: \n279:     # Deploy AgentRuntime CR\n280:     result = provider.deploy_agent_runtime(\n281:         agent_name=metadata.agent_name,\n282:         image_url=options.get(\"image_url\", \"\"),\n283:         port=metadata.port,\n284:         entrypoint=metadata.entrypoint,\n285:         env_vars={},\n286:         workload_manager_url=metadata.workload_manager_url,\n287:         router_url=metadata.router_url,\n288:         readiness_probe_path=metadata.readiness_probe_path,\n289:         readiness_probe_port=metadata.readiness_probe_port,\n290:     )\n291: \n292:     # Wait for CR readiness (poll status)\n293:     # ... polling logic ...\n294: \n295:     return {\n296:         \"agent_id\": result.get(\"name\"),\n297:         \"agent_endpoint\": result.get(\"endpoint\"),\n298:         \"namespace\": namespace,\n299:         \"k8s_deployment\": {\n300:             \"type\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n301:             \"namespace\": namespace,\n302:             \"cr_name\": result.get(\"name\"),\n303:         },\n304:     }\n305: ```\n306: \n307: ### 4.7 Kubernetes Provider Flow (_publish_k8s)\n308: \n309: ```python\n310: def _publish_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n311:     namespace = options.get(\"namespace\") or \"default\"\n312:     replicas = options.get(\"replicas\") or 1\n313:     node_port = options.get(\"node_port\")\n314: \n315:     provider = KubernetesProvider(namespace=namespace, verbose=self.verbose)\n316: \n317:     # Deploy Deployment + Service\n318:     result = provider.deploy_agent(\n319:         agent_name=metadata.agent_name,\n320:         image_url=options.get(\"image_url\", \"\"),\n321:         port=metadata.port,\n322:         entrypoint=metadata.entrypoint,\n323:         replicas=replicas,\n324:         node_port=node_port,\n325:         env_vars={},\n326:     )\n327: \n328:     # Wait for deployment readiness\n329:     try:\n330:         provider.wait_for_deployment_ready(result[\"deployment_name\"], timeout=120)\n331:     except TimeoutError:\n332:         raise RuntimeError(f\"Deployment {result['deployment_name']} did not become ready within 120s\")\n333: \n334:     return {\n335:         \"deployment_name\": result[\"deployment_name\"],\n336:         \"service_name\": result[\"service_name\"],\n337:         \"service_url\": result[\"service_url\"],\n338:         \"namespace\": namespace,\n339:         \"replicas\": replicas,\n340:         \"node_port\": result.get(\"node_port\"),\n341:         \"k8s_deployment\": {\n342:             \"type\": \"Deployment\",\n343:             \"namespace\": namespace,\n344:             \"deployment_name\": result[\"deployment_name\"],\n345:             \"service_url\": result[\"service_url\"],\n346:         },\n347:     }\n348: ```\n349: \n350: ### 4.8 _update_publish_metadata\n351: \n352: ```python\n353: def _update_publish_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, agent_info: Dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n354:     service = MetadataService(verbose=self.verbose)\n355:     updates = {\n356:         \"agent_id\": agent_info.get(\"agent_id\"),\n357:         \"agent_endpoint\": agent_info.get(\"agent_endpoint\") or agent_info.get(\"service_url\"),\n358:         \"k8s_deployment\": agent_info.get(\"k8s_deployment\"),\n359:     }\n360:     service.update_metadata(workspace_path, updates)\n361: ```\n362: \n363: ---\n364: \n365: ## Error Handling\n366: \n367: ### 5.1 Error Handling Strategy\n368: \n369: | Error Type | Handling | Exit Code |\n370: |------------|----------|-----------|\n371: | Workspace validation failure | `_handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)` | 1 |\n372: | Docker unavailable (local mode) | `_handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)` | 1 |\n373: | Missing image URL | `_handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)` | 1 |\n374: | Missing router_url/workload_manager_url (agentcube) | `_handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)` | 1 |\n375: | Invalid node_port range | `_handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)` | 1 |\n376: | Deployment readiness timeout | `_handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)` | 1 |\n377: | K8s client initialization failure | `_handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)` | 1 |\n378: \n379: ### 5.2 CLI Error Handler\n380: \n381: ```python\n382: def _handle_error(e: Exception, command_name: str, verbose: bool) -> None:\n383:     console.print(f\"[red]Error {command_name}: {e}[/red]\")\n384:     if verbose:\n385:         console.print_exception()\n386:     raise typer.Exit(1)\n387: ```\n388: \n389: ### 5.3 Verbose vs Global Verbose\n390: \n391: The subcommand's local `--verbose` flag is passed to `_handle_error`, ensuring traceback is printed even if global `-v` was not passed on the root callback.\n392: \n393: ---\n394: \n395: ## Testing Strategy\n396: \n397: ### 6.1 Unit Test Matrix\n398: \n399: #### PublishRuntime Tests (`tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py`)\n400: \n401: | Test Name | Description |\n402: |-----------|-------------|\n403: | `TestPublishRuntime_ValidAgentCubePublish` | Valid workspace, agentcube provider → publishes CR successfully |\n404: | `TestPublishRuntime_ValidK8sPublish` | Valid workspace, k8s provider → publishes Deployment + Service |\n405: | `TestPublishRuntime_MissingWorkspace` | Non-existent path → `ValueError` |\n406: | `TestPublishRuntime_MissingImageUrlLocal` | Local build mode, no image_url → `ValueError` |\n407: | `TestPublishRuntime_MissingRouterUrl` | AgentCube provider, no router_url → `ValueError` |\n408: | `TestPublishRuntime_MissingWorkloadManagerUrl` | AgentCube provider, no workload_manager_url → `ValueError` |\n409: | `TestPublishRuntime_InvalidNodePort` | node_port=9999 → `ValueError` |\n410: | `TestPublishRuntime_DockerUnavailable` | Local mode, Docker down → `RuntimeError` |\n411: | `TestPublishRuntime_CloudImageResolution` | Cloud mode, image URL from metadata → resolves correctly |\n412: | `TestPublishRuntime_MetadataUpdate` | Metadata updated with deployment info after publish |\n413: | `TestPublishRuntime_VersionOverride` | `--version` overrides metadata version |\n414: | `TestPublishRuntime_DeploymentTimeout` | K8s deployment not ready → `RuntimeError` |\n415: | `TestPublishRuntime_UnsupportedProvider` | provider=\"unknown\" → `ValueError` |\n416: | `TestPublishRuntime_UnsupportedBuildMode` | build_mode=\"unknown\" → `ValueError` |\n417: \n418: #### CLI Command Tests (`tests/cli/test_publish_command.py`)\n419: \n420: | Test Name | Description |\n421: |-----------|-------------|\n422: | `TestPublishCommand_SuccessAgentCube` | `publish --provider agentcube` → success output, exit 0 |\n423: | `TestPublishCommand_SuccessK8s` | `publish --provider k8s` → success output, exit 0 |\n424: | `TestPublishCommand_Defaults` | `publish` (no options) → uses defaults |\n425: | `TestPublishCommand_VerboseError` | Exception + `--verbose` → red error + traceback, exit 1 |\n426: | `TestPublishCommand_QuietError` | Exception, no `--verbose` → red error only, exit 1 |\n427: | `TestPublishCommand_ProgressSpinner` | Runs with Rich Progress spinner visible |\n428: \n429: #### AgentCubeProvider Tests (`tests/services/test_agentcube_provider.py`)\n430: \n431: | Test Name | Description |\n432: |-----------|-------------|\n433: | `TestAgentCubeProvider_DeployCR` | Creates AgentRuntime CR with correct spec |\n434: | `TestAgentCubeProvider_EnvVarFallback` | Missing env vars fall back to os.environ |\n435: | `TestAgentCubeProvider_SessionConfig` | CR has sessionTimeout=15m, maxSessionDuration=8h |\n436: | `TestAgentCubeProvider_ImagePullSecrets` | CR has imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}] |\n437: | `TestAgentCubeProvider_SanitizeName` | Invalid chars replaced, truncated to 63 chars |\n438: | `TestAgentCubeProvider_GetAgentRuntime` | Retrieves existing CR by name |\n439: \n440: #### KubernetesProvider Tests (`tests/services/test_k8s_provider.py`)\n441: \n442: | Test Name | Description |\n443: |-----------|-------------|\n444: | `TestK8sProvider_DeployAgent` | Creates Deployment + NodePort Service |\n445: | `TestK8sProvider_WaitForReady` | Waits until deployment ready, returns |\n446: | `TestK8sProvider_WaitTimeout` | Timeout exceeded → `TimeoutError` |\n447: | `TestK8sProvider_NodePortRange` | NodePort in 30000-32767 range |\n448: | `TestK8sProvider_ServiceUrl` | Service URL format: `http://localhost:{node_port}` |\n449: | `TestK8sProvider_DeleteAgent` | Deletes Deployment + Service, ignores 404 |\n450: \n451: ### 6.2 Test Helpers\n452: \n453: ```python\n454: @pytest.fixture\n455: def workspace_with_metadata(tmp_path: Path) -> Path:\n456:     ws = tmp_path / \"my-agent\"\n457:     ws.mkdir()\n458:     (ws / \"main.py\").write_text(\"print('hello')\\n\")\n459:     (ws / \"agent_metadata.yaml\").write_text(\n460:         \"agent_name: test-agent\\n\"\n461:         \"language: python\\n\"\n462:         \"entrypoint: python main.py\\n\"\n463:         \"port: 8080\\n\"\n464:         \"build_mode: local\\n\"\n465:         \"router_url: http://router.example.com\\n\"\n466:         \"workload_manager_url: http://wm.example.com\\n\"\n467:     )\n468:     return ws\n469: \n470: @pytest.fixture\n471: def mock_docker_service(mocker):\n472:     service = mocker.patch(\"agentcube.runtime.publish_runtime.DockerService\")\n473:     service.return_value.check_docker_available.return_value = True\n474:     service.return_value.push_image.return_value = {\"pushed_image\": \"registry.example.com/my-agent:v1.0.0\"}\n475:     return service\n476: \n477: @pytest.fixture\n478: def mock_agentcube_provider(mocker):\n479:     provider = mocker.patch(\"agentcube.runtime.publish_runtime.AgentCubeProvider\")\n480:     provider.return_value.deploy_agent_runtime.return_value = {\n481:         \"name\": \"test-agent\",\n482:         \"endpoint\": \"http://router.example.com/v1/...\",\n483:     }\n484:     return provider\n485: \n486: @pytest.fixture\n487: def mock_k8s_provider(mocker):\n488:     provider = mocker.patch(\"agentcube.runtime.publish_runtime.KubernetesProvider\")\n489:     provider.return_value.deploy_agent.return_value = {\n490:         \"deployment_name\": \"test-agent\",\n491:         \"service_name\": \"test-agent\",\n492:         \"service_url\": \"http://localhost:30080\",\n493:         \"node_port\": 30080,\n494:     }\n495:     return provider\n496: ```\n497: \n498: ### 6.3 Mock Strategy\n499: \n500: - **Filesystem:** Use `pytest` `tmp_path` fixture for isolated workspaces\n501: - **MetadataService:** Real instance (lightweight, no external deps)\n502: - **DockerService:** Mock `check_docker_available`, `push_image`, `_docker_login_sdk`\n503: - **AgentCubeProvider:** Mock `deploy_agent_runtime`, `get_agent_runtime`\n504: - **KubernetesProvider:** Mock `deploy_agent`, `wait_for_deployment_ready`, `get_agent_status`\n505: - **Console output:** Capture via `capfd` or `rich.console.Console(record=True)`\n506: \n507: ### 6.4 Gate Requirements\n508: \n509: 1. `pytest tests/ -v` all pass\n510: 2. `pytest tests/ --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing` coverage ≥ 80%\n511: 3. `ruff check agentcube/` no violations\n512: 4. `mypy agentcube/` no type errors\n513: 5. All PublishRuntime public methods have unit tests\n514: 6. Error paths tested (invalid workspace, missing URLs, bad node_port, timeout)\n515: 7. Both provider flows tested (agentcube and k8s)\n516: \n517: ---\n518: \n519: ## Implementation Notes\n520: \n521: 1. **Image preparation is provider-agnostic** — the same image URL is used regardless of target provider\n522: 2. **Metadata is the source of truth** — CLI options override metadata, but metadata is updated with final deployment state\n523: 3. **Namespace resolution order:** CLI option → metadata → default (\"default\")\n524: 4. **Version handling:** If `--version` provided, update metadata; otherwise use existing metadata version or \"latest\"\n525: 5. **Credential security:** Image credentials passed via CLI options are not logged even in verbose mode\n526: 6. **Concurrent deployments:** No locking mechanism; concurrent publishes to same namespace may cause conflicts\n527: 7. **CR status polling:** AgentCube provider polls CR status field for readiness; K8s provider uses `wait_for_deployment_ready` with 120s timeout\n528: 8. **NodePort validation:** Validated at CLI level (30000-32767) before reaching provider\n529: 9. **Environment variable fallback:** AgentCube provider falls back to `os.environ.get(\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\")` and `os.environ.get(\"ROUTER_URL\")` if not in metadata\n\n(End of file - total 529 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 — Design\n\n## Overview\n\nThe `publish` command deploys a packaged and built agent to a target Kubernetes cluster. It supports two providers:\n- **`agentcube`** (default): Deploys an AgentRuntime Custom Resource (CR) to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n- **`k8s`**: Deploys standard Kubernetes Deployment + NodePort Service\n\nThe command handles image preparation (local Docker push or cloud image URL), provider-specific deployment, metadata updates, and readiness verification. It is the third step in the agent lifecycle pipeline: `pack → build → publish → invoke`.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### 2.1 Data Flow\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                          CLI (Typer)                                  │\n│   kubectl-agentcube publish -f <workspace> [--provider agentcube]    │\n└────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                         │ options dict","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/design.md","time":{"start":1775855458007,"end":1775855458017}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775855459264,"sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","part":{"id":"prt_d793bd7590013lPDMgv6m8hYoa","messageID":"msg_d793bc17200152u5wPytVbUdIY","sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_dc7e752795cb4ba1ae12767c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-022: CLI publish 命令 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n6: - **Language:** Python\n7: - **Size:** L\n8: - **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: ### Requirement: `publish` command entry point\n13: \n14: The system SHALL provide a `publish` subcommand on the Typer application that orchestrates agent deployment to either AgentCube (AgentRuntime CR) or standard Kubernetes.\n15: \n16: #### Scenario: Command signature and options\n17: - **GIVEN** the CLI is installed and the user runs `agentcube publish --help`\n18: - **WHEN** the help text is displayed\n19: - **THEN** it SHALL show the following options:\n20:   - `-f, --workspace TEXT` — Path to the agent workspace directory (default: `.`)\n21:   - `--version TEXT` — Semantic version string (e.g., v1.0.0)\n22:   - `--image-url TEXT` — Image repository URL (required in local build mode)\n23:   - `--image-username TEXT` — Username for image repository\n24:   - `--image-password TEXT` — Password for image repository\n25:   - `--description TEXT` — Agent description\n26:   - `--region TEXT` — Deployment region\n27:   - `--cloud-provider TEXT` — Cloud provider name (e.g., huawei)\n28:   - `--provider TEXT` — Target provider: `agentcube` (AgentRuntime CR) or `k8s` (Deployment/Service) (default: `agentcube`)\n29:   - `--node-port INTEGER` — Specific NodePort to use (30000-32767) for K8s deployment\n30:   - `--replicas INTEGER` — Number of replicas for K8s deployment (default: 1)\n31:   - `--namespace TEXT` — The namespace for the deployment\n32:   - `--verbose` — Enable detailed logging\n33: \n34: #### Scenario: Default option values\n35: - **GIVEN** the user runs `agentcube publish` with no options\n36: - **WHEN** the command resolves its arguments\n37: - **THEN** the values SHALL be:\n38:   - `workspace` = `\".\"`\n39:   - `version` = `None`\n40:   - `image_url` = `None`\n41:   - `image_username` = `None`\n42:   - `image_password` = `None`\n43:   - `description` = `None`\n44:   - `region` = `None`\n45:   - `cloud_provider` = `None`\n46:   - `provider` = `\"agentcube\"`\n47:   - `node_port` = `None`\n48:   - `replicas` = `None`\n49:   - `namespace` = `None`\n50:   - `verbose` = `False`\n51: \n52: #### Scenario: Workspace path resolution\n53: - **GIVEN** the user provides a workspace path via `-f` or `--workspace`\n54: - **WHEN** the command starts execution\n55: - **THEN** the path SHALL be resolved to an absolute `Path` object before being passed to `PublishRuntime`\n56: \n57: ### Requirement: Provider validation\n58: \n59: The system SHALL validate the `--provider` option and route to the correct publish flow.\n60: \n61: #### Scenario: Valid provider values\n62: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--provider agentcube` or `--provider k8s`\n63: - **WHEN** the command validates the provider\n64: - **THEN** the system SHALL accept the value and instantiate `PublishRuntime` with the corresponding `provider` argument\n65: \n66: #### Scenario: Invalid provider value\n67: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--provider invalid-provider`\n68: - **WHEN** the command validates the provider\n69: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating the provider must be `agentcube` or `k8s`\n70: \n71: ### Requirement: Image preparation for publishing\n72: \n73: The system SHALL prepare the container image for deployment by either pushing a local image to a registry or using an explicit image URL from metadata.\n74: \n75: #### Scenario: Image preparation dispatch by build mode\n76: - **GIVEN** `PublishRuntime._prepare_image_for_publishing` is called\n77: - **WHEN** `metadata.build_mode` is `local`\n78: - **THEN** it SHALL call `_prepare_local_image` and return the resulting image reference\n79: - **WHEN** `metadata.build_mode` is `cloud`\n80: - **THEN** it SHALL call `_prepare_cloud_image` and return the resulting image reference\n81: \n82: #### Scenario: Local image preparation with CLI credentials\n83: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` is `local` and the user passes `--image-url`, `--image-username`, and `--image-password`\n84: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._prepare_local_image` runs\n85: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n86:   1. Call `DockerService._docker_login_sdk` with the provided credentials\n87:   2. Call `DockerService._tag_image_sdk` to tag the local image for the target registry\n88:   3. Call `DockerService.push_image` to push the image to the registry\n89:   4. Return the full image reference (registry URL + image name + tag)\n90: \n91: #### Scenario: Local image preparation without credentials\n92: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` is `local` and no `--image-username`/`--image-password` is provided\n93: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._prepare_local_image` runs\n94: - **THEN** it SHALL attempt to push using credentials from metadata (`registry_username`, `registry_password`) if present, or skip login if the registry allows anonymous push\n95: \n96: #### Scenario: Local image preparation requires image URL\n97: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` is `local` and no `--image-url` is provided\n98: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._prepare_local_image` runs\n99: - **THEN** it SHALL check metadata for `image` field; if absent, raise `ValueError` indicating image URL is required for local build mode\n100: \n101: #### Scenario: Cloud image preparation\n102: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` is `cloud`\n103: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._prepare_cloud_image` runs\n104: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n105:   1. Resolve the image reference from metadata `image` field or `--image-url`\n106:   2. Return the image reference without performing Docker operations\n107: \n108: ### Requirement: AgentCube provider (AgentRuntime CR) publish flow\n109: \n110: The system SHALL deploy an AgentRuntime custom resource to Kubernetes when `provider` is `agentcube`.\n111: \n112: #### Scenario: AgentCube prerequisites — required URLs\n113: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `agentcube`\n114: - **WHEN** metadata lacks `router_url` or `workload_manager_url`\n115: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError` with a message requiring both fields in `agent_metadata.yaml`\n116: \n117: #### Scenario: AgentCube prerequisites — readiness probe fields\n118: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `agentcube`\n119: - **WHEN** metadata lacks `readiness_probe_path` or `readiness_probe_port`\n120: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError` indicating readiness probe configuration is required\n121: \n122: #### Scenario: Successful AgentRuntime CR deployment\n123: - **GIVEN** all prerequisites are met and `provider` is `agentcube`\n124: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._publish_cr_to_k8s` runs\n125: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n126:   1. Prepare the image reference via `_prepare_image_for_publishing`\n127:   2. Call `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime` with `agent_name`, `image_url`, `port`, `entrypoint`, `env_vars`, `workload_manager_url`, `router_url`, `readiness_probe_path`, `readiness_probe_port`\n128:   3. Update metadata with deployment info via `_update_publish_metadata`\n129:   4. Return a dict with `status`, `agent_name`, `namespace`, `agent_id`\n130: \n131: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR deployment with namespace override\n132: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--namespace production`\n133: - **WHEN** `AgentCubeProvider` is instantiated\n134: - **THEN** it SHALL use `production` as the namespace instead of the default `default`\n135: \n136: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR deployment with version override\n137: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--version v2.0.0`\n138: - **WHEN** `_publish_cr_to_k8s` runs\n139: - **THEN** it SHALL update `metadata.version` to `v2.0.0` before deployment\n140: \n141: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR deployment with description override\n142: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--description \"My updated agent\"`\n143: - **WHEN** `_publish_cr_to_k8s` runs\n144: - **THEN** it SHALL update `metadata.description` before deployment\n145: \n146: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR deployment with region\n147: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--region cn-north-4`\n148: - **WHEN** `_publish_cr_to_k8s` runs\n149: - **THEN** it SHALL update `metadata.region` before deployment\n150: \n151: ### Requirement: Standard Kubernetes provider publish flow\n152: \n153: The system SHALL deploy a standard Kubernetes Deployment and NodePort Service when `provider` is `k8s`.\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: Successful K8s deployment\n156: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `k8s` and Kubernetes client initializes\n157: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._publish_k8s` runs\n158: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n159:   1. Prepare the image reference via `_prepare_image_for_publishing`\n160:   2. Call `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent` with `agent_name`, `image_url`, `port`, `entrypoint`, `replicas`, `node_port`, `env_vars`\n161:   3. Call `KubernetesProvider.wait_for_deployment_ready` with `timeout=120`\n162:   4. Update metadata with deployment info via `_update_publish_metadata`\n163:   5. Return a dict with `status`, `deployment_name`, `service_name`, `namespace`, `node_port`, `service_url`\n164: \n165: #### Scenario: K8s deployment with replicas override\n166: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--replicas 3`\n167: - **WHEN** `_publish_k8s` calls `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent`\n168: - **THEN** it SHALL pass `replicas=3` instead of the default `1`\n169: \n170: #### Scenario: K8s deployment with NodePort override\n171: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--node-port 30080`\n172: - **WHEN** `_publish_k8s` calls `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent`\n173: - **THEN** it SHALL pass `node_port=30080` and the resulting `service_url` SHALL be `http://localhost:30080`\n174: \n175: #### Scenario: K8s deployment readiness timeout\n176: - **GIVEN** the deployment does not become ready within 120 seconds\n177: - **WHEN** `KubernetesProvider.wait_for_deployment_ready` exceeds the timeout\n178: - **THEN** it SHALL raise `TimeoutError` and the system SHALL record the error in metadata before raising `RuntimeError`\n179: \n180: #### Scenario: K8s deployment with namespace override\n181: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--namespace staging`\n182: - **WHEN** `KubernetesProvider` is instantiated\n183: - **THEN** it SHALL use `staging` as the namespace for all resource creation\n184: \n185: ### Requirement: Publish metadata update\n186: \n187: The system SHALL update workspace metadata with publish results upon successful deployment.\n188: \n189: #### Scenario: Update publish metadata on success\n190: - **GIVEN** a successful publish (either provider)\n191: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._update_publish_metadata` runs\n192: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n193:   1. Update `metadata.agent_id` with the assigned agent ID\n194:   2. Update `metadata.agent_endpoint` with the service URL\n195:   3. Update `metadata.k8s_deployment` with provider-specific deployment info\n196:   4. Persist the updated metadata to `agent_metadata.yaml` via `MetadataService.save_metadata`\n197: \n198: #### Scenario: K8s deployment metadata structure\n199: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `k8s` and publish succeeds\n200: - **WHEN** `_update_publish_metadata` runs\n201: - **THEN** `metadata.k8s_deployment` SHALL include:\n202:   - `type`: `\"Deployment\"`\n203:   - `deployment_name`: the deployment name\n204:   - `service_name`: the service name\n205:   - `namespace`: the namespace\n206:   - `node_port`: the assigned NodePort\n207:   - `service_url`: the service URL\n208: \n209: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR metadata structure\n210: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `agentcube` and publish succeeds\n211: - **WHEN** `_update_publish_metadata` runs\n212: - **THEN** `metadata.k8s_deployment` SHALL include:\n213:   - `type`: `\"AgentRuntime\"`\n214:   - `agent_name`: the agent name\n215:   - `namespace`: the namespace\n216:   - `agent_id`: the assigned agent ID\n217: \n218: ### Requirement: CLI success output\n219: \n220: The system SHALL display a Rich-formatted success message after a successful publish.\n221: \n222: #### Scenario: Successful publish output — AgentCube provider\n223: - **GIVEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` completes without exception with `provider=agentcube`\n224: - **WHEN** the `publish` command finishes\n225: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print:\n226:   - A success message with the agent name\n227:   - The resolved workspace path\n228:   - The agent ID\n229:   - The agent endpoint URL\n230:   - Using Rich markup for formatting\n231: \n232: #### Scenario: Successful publish output — K8s provider\n233: - **GIVEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` completes without exception with `provider=k8s`\n234: - **WHEN** the `publish` command finishes\n235: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print:\n236:   - A success message with the agent name\n237:   - The resolved workspace path\n238:   - The deployment name and service name\n239:   - The service URL (e.g., `http://localhost:{node_port}`)\n240:   - Using Rich markup for formatting\n241: \n242: #### Scenario: Verbose publish output\n243: - **GIVEN** `--verbose` is passed\n244: - **WHEN** the publish runs\n245: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL display detailed logging including:\n246:   - Provider selection\n247:   - Image preparation steps\n248:   - Deployment progress\n249:   - Metadata update confirmation\n250: \n251: ### Requirement: Error handling\n252: \n253: The system SHALL handle publish failures gracefully with appropriate error messages.\n254: \n255: #### Scenario: Publish error with verbose flag\n256: - **GIVEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` raises an exception\n257: - **WHEN** `--verbose` is `True`\n258: - **THEN** `_handle_error` SHALL:\n259:   1. Print `Error publishing agent: {e}` in red\n260:   2. Print a full traceback\n261:   3. Exit with code `1`\n262: \n263: #### Scenario: Publish error without verbose flag\n264: - **GIVEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` raises an exception\n265: - **WHEN** `--verbose` is `False`\n266: - **THEN** `_handle_error` SHALL:\n267:   1. Print `Error publishing agent: {e}` in red\n268:   2. Exit with code `1` (no traceback)\n269: \n270: #### Scenario: Missing workspace\n271: - **GIVEN** the workspace path does not exist\n272: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` is called\n273: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` with a message indicating the workspace directory does not exist\n274: \n275: #### Scenario: Missing metadata file\n276: - **GIVEN** `agent_metadata.yaml` does not exist in the workspace\n277: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` attempts to load metadata\n278: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating the workspace must be packaged first\n279: \n280: ### Requirement: Progress indication\n281: \n282: The system SHALL display a Rich `Progress` spinner during the publish operation.\n283: \n284: #### Scenario: Progress spinner during publish\n285: - **GIVEN** the publish command is running\n286: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` is executing\n287: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL show a Rich `Progress` spinner with the text `\"Publishing agent...\"`\n288: \n289: #### Scenario: Progress completion\n290: - **GIVEN** the publish completes successfully\n291: - **WHEN** the spinner stops\n292: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL replace the spinner with a success checkmark and summary\n293: \n294: ### Requirement: NodePort validation\n295: \n296: The system SHALL validate the `--node-port` value when provided for K8s deployments.\n297: \n298: #### Scenario: Valid NodePort range\n299: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--node-port 30080`\n300: - **WHEN** the command validates the node port\n301: - **THEN** the system SHALL accept the value (within 30000-32767 range)\n302: \n303: #### Scenario: Invalid NodePort — below range\n304: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--node-port 29999`\n305: - **WHEN** the command validates the node port\n306: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating NodePort must be between 30000 and 32767\n307: \n308: #### Scenario: Invalid NodePort — above range\n309: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--node-port 32768`\n310: - **WHEN** the command validates the node port\n311: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating NodePort must be between 30000 and 32767\n312: \n313: ## File changes\n314: \n315: | Action | File | Description |\n316: |--------|------|-------------|\n317: | Modify | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Add `publish` Typer command with options, provider routing, and error handling |\n318: | Modify | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | Implement `publish`, `_publish_cr_to_k8s`, `_publish_k8s`, `_prepare_image_for_publishing`, `_prepare_local_image`, `_prepare_cloud_image`, `_update_publish_metadata` |\n319: | Modify | `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | Ensure `push_image`, `_docker_login_sdk`, `_tag_image_sdk` support publish workflow |\n320: | Modify | `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | Ensure `deploy_agent_runtime` supports all publish parameters |\n321: | Modify | `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | Ensure `deploy_agent` and `wait_for_deployment_ready` support publish workflow |\n322: | Modify | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | Ensure metadata save supports publish workflow |\n323: | Add | `tests/cli/test_publish.py` | CLI publish command tests |\n324: | Add | `tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py` | PublishRuntime unit tests |\n\n(End of file - total 324 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022: CLI publish 命令 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n- **Language:** Python\n- **Size:** L\n- **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: `publish` command entry point\n\nThe system SHALL provide a `publish` subcommand on the Typer application that orchestrates agent deployment to either AgentCube (AgentRuntime CR) or standard Kubernetes.\n\n#### Scenario: Command signature and options\n- **GIVEN** the CLI is installed and the user runs `agentcube publish --help`\n- **WHEN** the help text is displayed\n- **THEN** it SHALL show the following options:\n  - `-f, --workspace TEXT` — Path to the agent workspace directory (default: `.`)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775855459253,"end":1775855459262}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775855460567,"sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","part":{"id":"prt_d793bdc42001aI2jJlPop9Z4rF","messageID":"msg_d793bc17200152u5wPytVbUdIY","sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_b81f20e3af284d9dbca7f290","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** cmd/cli\n4: > **Language:** Python\n5: > **Size:** L\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-022/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-022/design.md`, `changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. 扩展 DockerService — 镜像推送支持\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 在 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` 中实现 `push_image(self, image_tag: str, registry_url: str, username: Optional[str] = None, password: Optional[str] = None) -> Dict[str, str]`：\n12:   - 使用 `docker.from_env()` 创建客户端\n13:   - 调用 `client.images.push(repository, tag, auth_config)` 推送镜像\n14:   - 返回 `{\"pushed_image\": image_tag, \"status\": \"success\"}`\n15: - [ ] 1.2 实现 `_docker_login_sdk(self, registry_url: str, username: str, password: str) -> bool`：\n16:   - 调用 `client.login(username, password, registry_url)`\n17:   - 成功返回 `True`，失败抛出异常\n18: - [ ] 1.3 实现 `_tag_image_sdk(self, source_image: str, target_image: str) -> bool`：\n19:   - 调用 `client.images.get(source_image).tag(target_image)`\n20:   - 成功返回 `True`\n21: - [ ] 1.4 在 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py` 中添加测试：\n22:   - `TestDockerService_PushImage_Success`：成功推送 → 返回正确结果\n23:   - `TestDockerService_PushImage_WithCredentials`：带 credentials 推送 → `auth_config` 正确传递\n24:   - `TestDockerService_PushImage_Failure`：推送失败 → 抛出 `docker.errors.APIError`\n25:   - `TestDockerService_DockerLoginSdk_Success`：登录成功 → 返回 `True`\n26:   - `TestDockerService_DockerLoginSdk_Failure`：登录失败 → 抛出异常\n27:   - `TestDockerService_TagImageSdk_Success`：tag 成功 → 返回 `True`\n28: \n29: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py -v` 全部通过\n30: \n31: ---\n32: \n33: ## T2. 实现 AgentCubeProvider — AgentRuntime CR 部署\n34: \n35: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`\n36: - [ ] 2.2 定义 `AgentCubeProvider` 类：`__init__(self, namespace: str = \"default\", verbose: bool = False)`\n37: - [ ] 2.3 实现 `deploy_agent_runtime(self, agent_name: str, image_url: str, port: int, entrypoint: str, env_vars: Dict[str, str], workload_manager_url: str, router_url: str, readiness_probe_path: str, readiness_probe_port: int) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n38:   - 初始化 K8s client（`kubernetes.client.CustomObjectsApi`）\n39:   - 构造 AgentRuntime CR spec（`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`）\n40:   - CR 包含：image、port、entrypoint、env、workload_manager_url、router_url、readinessProbe\n41:   - sessionTimeout=15m、maxSessionDuration=8h\n42:   - imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]\n43:   - 调用 `create_namespaced_custom_object` 创建 CR\n44:   - 返回 `{\"name\": sanitized_name, \"endpoint\": router_url + \"/v1/...\"}`\n45: - [ ] 2.4 实现 `_sanitize_name(self, name: str) -> str`：\n46:   - 将无效字符替换为 `-`\n47:   - 截断至 63 字符（K8s 名称限制）\n48: - [ ] 2.5 实现 `get_agent_runtime(self, name: str) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]`：\n49:   - 调用 `get_namespaced_custom_object` 获取现有 CR\n50:   - 不存在时返回 `None`\n51: - [ ] 2.6 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_agentcube_provider.py`\n52: - [ ] 2.7 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_DeployCR`：创建 AgentRuntime CR，spec 正确\n53: - [ ] 2.8 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_EnvVarFallback`：缺失 env vars 时 fallback 到 `os.environ`\n54: - [ ] 2.9 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_SessionConfig`：CR 包含 sessionTimeout=15m, maxSessionDuration=8h\n55: - [ ] 2.10 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_ImagePullSecrets`：CR 包含 imagePullSecrets\n56: - [ ] 2.11 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_SanitizeName`：无效字符替换，截断至 63 字符\n57: - [ ] 2.12 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_GetAgentRuntime`：获取现有 CR\n58: \n59: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_agentcube_provider.py -v` 全部通过\n60: \n61: ---\n62: \n63: ## T3. 实现 KubernetesProvider — Deployment + NodePort Service 部署\n64: \n65: - [ ] 3.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`\n66: - [ ] 3.2 定义 `KubernetesProvider` 类：`__init__(self, namespace: str = \"default\", verbose: bool = False)`\n67: - [ ] 3.3 实现 `deploy_agent(self, agent_name: str, image_url: str, port: int, entrypoint: str, replicas: int = 1, node_port: Optional[int] = None, env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n68:   - 初始化 K8s client（`kubernetes.client.AppsV1Api`, `CoreV1Api`）\n69:   - 创建 Deployment（container: image, port, entrypoint, env, replicas）\n70:   - 创建 NodePort Service（port 映射，node_port 指定或自动分配）\n71:   - 返回 `{\"deployment_name\": name, \"service_name\": name, \"service_url\": f\"http://localhost:{actual_node_port}\", \"node_port\": actual_node_port}`\n72: - [ ] 3.4 实现 `wait_for_deployment_ready(self, deployment_name: str, timeout: int = 120) -> None`：\n73:   - 轮询 Deployment status（`read_namespaced_deployment_status`）\n74:   - 检查 `ready_replicas == replicas`\n75:   - 超时则抛出 `TimeoutError`\n76: - [ ] 3.5 实现 `delete_agent(self, agent_name: str) -> None`：\n77:   - 删除 Deployment + Service\n78:   - 404 时忽略（`client.rest.ApiException` status=404）\n79: - [ ] 3.6 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_k8s_provider.py`\n80: - [ ] 3.7 测试 `TestK8sProvider_DeployAgent`：创建 Deployment + NodePort Service\n81: - [ ] 3.8 测试 `TestK8sProvider_WaitForReady`：等待至 ready 后返回\n82: - [ ] 3.9 测试 `TestK8sProvider_WaitTimeout`：超时 → `TimeoutError`\n83: - [ ] 3.10 测试 `TestK8sProvider_NodePortRange`：NodePort 在 30000-32767 范围\n84: - [ ] 3.11 测试 `TestK8sProvider_ServiceUrl`：URL 格式 `http://localhost:{node_port}`\n85: - [ ] 3.12 测试 `TestK8sProvider_DeleteAgent`：删除 Deployment + Service，忽略 404\n86: \n87: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_k8s_provider.py -v` 全部通过\n88: \n89: ---\n90: \n91: ## T4. 实现 PublishRuntime 类骨架与 publish() 主编排方法\n92: \n93: - [ ] 4.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`\n94: - [ ] 4.2 定义 `PublishRuntime` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\")`，存储 `self.verbose` 和 `self.provider`\n95: - [ ] 4.3 实现 `publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]` 主编排方法：\n96:   - 1. 校验 workspace 路径存在且为目录 → 否则 `ValueError`\n97:   - 2. 加载元数据：`metadata = MetadataService(verbose=self.verbose).load_metadata(workspace_path)`，如为 None 则 `ValueError(\"Workspace has not been packaged. Run 'pack' first.\")`\n98:   - 3. 应用 CLI 选项覆盖：遍历 `[\"version\", \"description\", \"region\"]`，非 None 则 `setattr(metadata, key, value)`\n99:   - 4. 校验 node_port 范围（如提供）：不在 30000-32767 → `ValueError(\"NodePort must be between 30000 and 32767\")`\n100:   - 5. 准备镜像：`image_url = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options)`\n101:   - 6. 路由到 provider：`agentcube` → `_publish_cr_to_k8s()`，`k8s` → `_publish_k8s()`，其他 → `ValueError`\n102:   - 7. 更新元数据：`self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, result)`\n103:   - 8. 返回 result\n104: - [ ] 4.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py`\n105: - [ ] 4.5 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_MissingWorkspace`：路径不存在 → `ValueError`\n106: - [ ] 4.6 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_UnpackagedWorkspace`：无 `agent_metadata.yaml` → `ValueError(\"Workspace has not been packaged...\")`\n107: - [ ] 4.7 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_UnsupportedProvider`：provider=\"unknown\" → `ValueError`\n108: - [ ] 4.8 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_UnsupportedBuildMode`：build_mode=\"unknown\" → `ValueError`\n109: - [ ] 4.9 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_InvalidNodePort_Below`：node_port=29999 → `ValueError`\n110: - [ ] 4.10 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_InvalidNodePort_Above`：node_port=32768 → `ValueError`\n111: - [ ] 4.11 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_VersionOverride`：`--version v2.0.0` → metadata.version 更新\n112: - [ ] 4.12 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_DescriptionOverride`：`--description` → metadata.description 更新\n113: - [ ] 4.13 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_RegionOverride`：`--region cn-north-4` → metadata.region 更新\n114: \n115: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py -v -k \"MissingWorkspace or UnpackagedWorkspace or UnsupportedProvider or UnsupportedBuildMode or InvalidNodePort or Override\"` 全部通过（T5-T7 方法可用 mock 替代）\n116: \n117: ---\n118: \n119: ## T5. 实现镜像准备流程 — PublishRuntime._prepare_image_for_publishing 及子方法\n120: \n121: - [ ] 5.1 实现 `_prepare_image_for_publishing(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str`：\n122:   - `metadata.build_mode == \"local\"` → 调用 `_prepare_local_image`\n123:   - `metadata.build_mode == \"cloud\"` → 调用 `_prepare_cloud_image`\n124:   - 其他 → `ValueError(f\"Unsupported build mode: {metadata.build_mode}\")`\n125: - [ ] 5.2 实现 `_prepare_local_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str`：\n126:   - 创建 `DockerService` 实例\n127:   - 检查 Docker 可用性 → 不可用则 `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")`\n128:   - 检查 `image_url`（CLI 选项）→ 无则检查 metadata.image → 仍无则 `ValueError(\"Image URL is required for local build mode\")`\n129:   - 构建 image_tag：`f\"{image_url}:{metadata.version or 'latest'}\"`\n130:   - 如提供 credentials（CLI 或 metadata）→ 调用 `docker_service._docker_login_sdk`\n131:   - 调用 `docker_service.push_image` 推送\n132:   - 返回推送后的 image reference\n133: - [ ] 5.3 实现 `_prepare_cloud_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str`：\n134:   - 优先使用 `options.get(\"image_url\")`\n135:   - 其次使用 `metadata.image.get(\"url\")`\n136:   - 均无则 `ValueError(\"Image URL is required for cloud build mode\")`\n137:   - 返回 image reference（不执行 Docker 操作）\n138: - [ ] 5.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_image.py`\n139: - [ ] 5.5 测试 `TestPrepareImage_LocalMode_Success`：local 模式，Docker 可用，image_url 提供 → 推送成功\n140: - [ ] 5.6 测试 `TestPrepareImage_LocalMode_NoImageUrl`：local 模式，无 image_url → `ValueError`\n141: - [ ] 5.7 测试 `TestPrepareImage_LocalMode_DockerUnavailable`：local 模式，Docker 不可用 → `RuntimeError`\n142: - [ ] 5.8 测试 `TestPrepareImage_LocalMode_WithCredentials`：提供 credentials → `_docker_login_sdk` 被调用\n143: - [ ] 5.9 测试 `TestPrepareImage_LocalMode_MetadataCredentials`：CLI 无 credentials，metadata 有 → 使用 metadata credentials\n144: - [ ] 5.10 测试 `TestPrepareImage_CloudMode_Success`：cloud 模式，image_url 提供 → 直接返回\n145: - [ ] 5.11 测试 `TestPrepareImage_CloudMode_FromMetadata`：cloud 模式，image URL 从 metadata.image[\"url\"] 解析\n146: - [ ] 5.12 测试 `TestPrepareImage_CloudMode_NoUrl`：cloud 模式，无 image URL → `ValueError`\n147: - [ ] 5.13 测试 `TestPrepareImage_UnknownBuildMode`：build_mode=\"unknown\" → `ValueError`\n148: - [ ] 5.14 测试 `TestPrepareImage_Dispatch_Local`：build_mode=\"local\" → 调用 `_prepare_local_image`\n149: - [ ] 5.15 测试 `TestPrepareImage_Dispatch_Cloud`：build_mode=\"cloud\" → 调用 `_prepare_cloud_image`\n150: \n151: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_image.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Image preparation 全部场景\n152: \n153: ---\n154: \n155: ## T6. 实现 AgentCube provider 发布流程 — PublishRuntime._publish_cr_to_k8s\n156: \n157: - [ ] 6.1 实现 `_publish_cr_to_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n158:   - 校验 prerequisites：`metadata.router_url` 和 `metadata.workload_manager_url` 均存在 → 否则 `ValueError(\"router_url and workload_manager_url are required...\")`\n159:   - 校验 readiness probe：`metadata.readiness_probe_path` 和 `metadata.readiness_probe_port` 均存在 → 否则 `ValueError`\n160:   - 初始化 `AgentCubeProvider(namespace=options.get(\"namespace\") or \"default\", verbose=self.verbose)`\n161:   - 调用 `provider.deploy_agent_runtime(agent_name, image_url, port, entrypoint, env_vars, workload_manager_url, router_url, readiness_probe_path, readiness_probe_port)`\n162:   - 返回 `{\"agent_id\": result[\"name\"], \"agent_endpoint\": result[\"endpoint\"], \"namespace\": namespace, \"k8s_deployment\": {\"type\": \"AgentRuntime\", \"namespace\": namespace, \"cr_name\": result[\"name\"]}}`\n163: - [ ] 6.2 在 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py` 中添加测试：\n164:   - `TestPublishRuntime_ValidAgentCubePublish`：有效 workspace，agentcube provider → 成功发布 CR\n165:   - `TestPublishRuntime_MissingRouterUrl`：agentcube provider，无 router_url → `ValueError`\n166:   - `TestPublishRuntime_MissingWorkloadManagerUrl`：agentcube provider，无 workload_manager_url → `ValueError`\n167:   - `TestPublishRuntime_MissingReadinessProbePath`：agentcube provider，无 readiness_probe_path → `ValueError`\n168:   - `TestPublishRuntime_MissingReadinessProbePort`：agentcube provider，无 readiness_probe_port → `ValueError`\n169:   - `TestPublishRuntime_AgentCubeWithNamespace`：`--namespace production` → 使用指定 namespace\n170: - [ ] 6.3 在 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_metadata.py` 中添加测试：\n171:   - `TestPublishRuntime_AgentCubeMetadataUpdate`：发布成功后 metadata 包含 agent_id, agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment（type=\"AgentRuntime\"）\n172: \n173: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py -v -k \"AgentCube\"` 全部通过\n174: \n175: ---\n176: \n177: ## T7. 实现 K8s provider 发布流程 — PublishRuntime._publish_k8s\n178: \n179: - [ ] 7.1 实现 `_publish_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n180:   - 解析 `namespace = options.get(\"namespace\") or \"default\"`\n181:   - 解析 `replicas = options.get(\"replicas\") or 1`\n182:   - 解析 `node_port = options.get(\"node_port\")`\n183:   - 初始化 `KubernetesProvider(namespace=namespace, verbose=self.verbose)`\n184:   - 调用 `provider.deploy_agent(agent_name, image_url, port, entrypoint, replicas, node_port, env_vars)`\n185:   - 调用 `provider.wait_for_deployment_ready(deployment_name, timeout=120)`\n186:   - 超时则 `RuntimeError(f\"Deployment {name} did not become ready within 120s\")`\n187:   - 返回 `{\"deployment_name\": result[\"deployment_name\"], \"service_name\": result[\"service_name\"], \"service_url\": result[\"service_url\"], \"namespace\": namespace, \"replicas\": replicas, \"node_port\": result[\"node_port\"], \"k8s_deployment\": {\"type\": \"Deployment\", \"namespace\": namespace, \"deployment_name\": result[\"deployment_name\"], \"service_url\": result[\"service_url\"]}}`\n188: - [ ] 7.2 在 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py` 中添加测试：\n189:   - `TestPublishRuntime_ValidK8sPublish`：有效 workspace，k8s provider → 成功发布 Deployment + Service\n190:   - `TestPublishRuntime_DeploymentTimeout`：K8s 部署未 ready → `RuntimeError`\n191:   - `TestPublishRuntime_K8sWithReplicas`：`--replicas 3` → 传递 replicas=3\n192:   - `TestPublishRuntime_K8sWithNodePort`：`--node-port 30080` → service_url 为 `http://localhost:30080`\n193:   - `TestPublishRuntime_K8sWithNamespace`：`--namespace staging` → 使用指定 namespace\n194: - [ ] 7.3 在 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_metadata.py` 中添加测试：\n195:   - `TestPublishRuntime_K8sMetadataUpdate`：发布成功后 metadata 包含 k8s_deployment（type=\"Deployment\", deployment_name, service_url）\n196: \n197: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py -v -k \"K8s\"` 全部通过\n198: \n199: ---\n200: \n201: ## T8. 实现发布元数据更新 — PublishRuntime._update_publish_metadata\n202: \n203: - [ ] 8.1 实现 `_update_publish_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, agent_info: Dict[str, Any]) -> None`：\n204:   - 创建 `MetadataService(verbose=self.verbose)` 实例\n205:   - 构造 updates dict：\n206:     ```python\n207:     updates = {\n208:         \"agent_id\": agent_info.get(\"agent_id\"),\n209:         \"agent_endpoint\": agent_info.get(\"agent_endpoint\") or agent_info.get(\"service_url\"),\n210:         \"k8s_deployment\": agent_info.get(\"k8s_deployment\"),\n211:     }\n212:     ```\n213:   - 调用 `service.update_metadata(workspace_path, updates)`\n214: - [ ] 8.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_metadata.py`\n215: - [ ] 8.3 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_AgentCube`：agentcube 发布 → metadata.agent_id, agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment.type=\"AgentRuntime\"\n216: - [ ] 8.4 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_K8s`：k8s 发布 → metadata.agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment.type=\"Deployment\"\n217: - [ ] 8.5 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_Persisted`：更新后重新加载 → 数据一致\n218: - [ ] 8.6 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_ServiceUrlFallback`：无 agent_endpoint 时使用 service_url\n219: - [ ] 8.7 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_K8sDeploymentStructure`：k8s_deployment 包含 type, deployment_name, namespace, service_url\n220: - [ ] 8.8 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_AgentCubeDeploymentStructure`：k8s_deployment 包含 type, agent_name, namespace, agent_id\n221: \n222: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_metadata.py -v` 全部通过\n223: \n224: ---\n225: \n226: ## T9. 实现 CLI publish 命令入口 — agentcube/cli/main.py\n227: \n228: - [ ] 9.1 在 `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` 中添加导入：\n229:   - `from agentcube.runtime.publish_runtime import PublishRuntime`\n230: - [ ] 9.2 实现 `@app.command()` publish 命令，选项：\n231:   - `workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", ...)`\n232:   - `version: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--version\", ...)`\n233:   - `image_url: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-url\", ...)`\n234:   - `image_username: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-username\", ...)`\n235:   - `image_password: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-password\", ...)`\n236:   - `description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--description\", ...)`\n237:   - `region: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--region\", ...)`\n238:   - `cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\", ...)`\n239:   - `provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\", ...)`\n240:   - `node_port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--node-port\", ...)`\n241:   - `replicas: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--replicas\", ...)`\n242:   - `namespace: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--namespace\", ...)`\n243:   - `verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", ...)`\n244: - [ ] 9.3 命令体：\n245:   - 校验 workspace 路径存在且为目录 → 否则 `ValueError`\n246:   - 校验 provider 值（`agentcube` 或 `k8s`）→ 否则 `ValueError`\n247:   - 校验 node_port 范围（如提供）→ 30000-32767，否则 `ValueError`\n248:   - 使用 Rich `Progress` + `SpinnerColumn` 显示 `\"Publishing agent...\"`\n249:   - 调用 `PublishRuntime(verbose=verbose, provider=provider).publish(workspace_path, **options)`\n250:   - 成功时 Rich 输出（agentcube provider）：agent name, workspace path, agent ID, endpoint URL\n251:   - 成功时 Rich 输出（k8s provider）：agent name, workspace path, deployment name, service name, service URL\n252:   - 异常时调用 `_handle_error(e, \"publishing agent\", verbose)`\n253: - [ ] 9.4 更新 `agentcube/__init__.py` 导出：添加 `PublishRuntime`\n254: - [ ] 9.5 更新 `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` 重新导出 `PublishRuntime`\n255: - [ ] 9.6 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_publish_command.py`\n256: - [ ] 9.7 测试 `TestPublishCommand_DefaultOptions`：无选项 → workspace=\".\", provider=\"agentcube\"\n257: - [ ] 9.8 测试 `TestPublishCommand_CustomWorkspace`：`-f /path` → 使用指定路径\n258: - [ ] 9.9 测试 `TestPublishCommand_AllOptions`：传递全部选项 → 正确传递给 PublishRuntime\n259: - [ ] 9.10 测试 `TestPublishCommand_SuccessAgentCube`：agentcube provider → 成功输出 agent name, agent ID, endpoint\n260: - [ ] 9.11 测试 `TestPublishCommand_SuccessK8s`：k8s provider → 成功输出 deployment name, service name, service URL\n261: - [ ] 9.12 测试 `TestPublishCommand_ErrorNoVerbose`：失败无 verbose → 红色错误，无 traceback，exit 1\n262: - [ ] 9.13 测试 `TestPublishCommand_ErrorVerbose`：失败有 verbose → 红色错误 + traceback，exit 1\n263: - [ ] 9.14 测试 `TestPublishCommand_ProgressSpinner`：执行期间显示 Progress spinner\n264: - [ ] 9.15 测试 `TestPublishCommand_HelpOutput`：`publish --help` 显示全部 13 个选项\n265: - [ ] 9.16 测试 `TestPublishCommand_InvalidProvider`：`--provider invalid` → `ValueError`\n266: - [ ] 9.17 测试 `TestPublishCommand_InvalidNodePort`：`--node-port 9999` → `ValueError`\n267: \n268: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_publish_command.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §CLI success output、§Error handling、§Progress indication 全部场景\n269: \n270: ---\n271: \n272: ## T10. 端到端集成测试\n273: \n274: - [ ] 10.1 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/integration/test_publish_e2e.py`\n275: - [ ] 10.2 测试 `TestPublishE2E_AgentCube_FullFlow`：对已 pack+build 的 hello-agent 运行 publish（agentcube provider，mock K8s）→ 成功\n276: - [ ] 10.3 测试 `TestPublishE2E_K8s_FullFlow`：对已 pack+build 的工作区运行 publish（k8s provider，mock K8s）→ 成功\n277: - [ ] 10.4 测试 `TestPublishE2E_UnpackagedWorkspace`：对未 pack 的工作区运行 publish → 错误退出\n278: - [ ] 10.5 测试 `TestPublishE2E_CliOverrides`：使用 `--version`, `--namespace`, `--replicas` 覆盖 → 正确传递\n279: - [ ] 10.6 测试 `TestPublishE2E_InvalidWorkspace`：对非目录路径运行 publish → 错误退出\n280: - [ ] 10.7 测试 `TestPublishE2E_MetadataUpdated`：publish 成功后 → `agent_metadata.yaml` 包含 agent_id, agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment\n281: - [ ] 10.8 测试 `TestPublishE2E_LocalModeImagePush`：local build mode + `--image-url` → 镜像推送流程触发（mock Docker）\n282: \n283: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/integration/test_publish_e2e.py -v` 全部通过（K8s/Docker 依赖的测试可标记 skip）\n284: \n285: ---\n286: \n287: ## T11. 代码质量门禁与最终验证\n288: \n289: - [ ] 11.1 运行 `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认无 lint 错误\n290: - [ ] 11.2 运行 `ruff format --check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认格式合规\n291: - [ ] 11.3 运行 `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认无类型错误\n292: - [ ] 11.4 运行 `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing` 确认覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n293: - [ ] 11.5 确认 T/C 比率 > 0.4（测试代码行数 / 源代码行数）\n294: - [ ] 11.6 运行 `pip install -e cmd/cli[dev]` 确认安装成功\n295: - [ ] 11.7 运行 `kubectl-agentcube --help` 确认帮助输出包含 publish 命令\n296: - [ ] 11.8 运行 `kubectl-agentcube publish --help` 确认 publish 选项完整（workspace, version, image-url, image-username, image-password, description, region, cloud-provider, provider, node-port, replicas, namespace, verbose）\n297: - [ ] 11.9 确认 `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` 有对应测试文件\n298: - [ ] 11.10 确认 `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` 有对应测试文件\n299: - [ ] 11.11 确认 `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` 有对应测试文件\n300: - [ ] 11.12 确认 `agentcube/cli/main.py` 的 publish 命令有对应测试文件\n301: - [ ] 11.13 确认 `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` 的 push_image 等方法有对应测试\n302: - [ ] 11.14 确认无 `print()` 用于业务逻辑输出（仅使用 Rich console）\n303: - [ ] 11.15 确认 credentials（image_username, image_password）不在 verbose 日志中泄露\n304: \n305: **Verification:** 以上 15 项全部通过；exit code 均为 0\n306: \n307: ---\n308: \n309: ## Task Dependencies\n310: \n311: ```\n312: T1 (DockerService 扩展) ──────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n313:                                                                       │\n314: T2 (AgentCubeProvider) ───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n315:                                                                       │\n316: T3 (KubernetesProvider) ──────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n317:                                                                       │\n318: T4 (PublishRuntime 骨架 + publish 编排) ←─────────────────────────────┤\n319:   │                                                                   │\n320:   ├── T5 (镜像准备流程) ←── T1 ───────────────────────────────────────┤\n321:   │                                                                   │\n322:   ├── T6 (AgentCube CR 发布) ←── T2 ──────────────────────────────────┤\n323:   │                                                                   │\n324:   ├── T7 (K8s Deployment 发布) ←── T3 ────────────────────────────────┤\n325:   │                                                                   │\n326:   └── T8 (元数据更新) ────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n327:                                                                       │\n328: T9 (CLI publish 命令) ←── T4, T5, T6, T7, T8 ─────────────────────────┘\n329:   │\n330: T10 (E2E 集成测试) ←── T9 ────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n331:   │\n332: T11 (质量门禁)\n333: ```\n334: \n335: **Parallel execution:**\n336: - T1（DockerService 扩展）可独立开始，不依赖其他任务\n337: - T2（AgentCubeProvider）可独立开始，不依赖其他任务\n338: - T3（KubernetesProvider）可独立开始，不依赖其他任务\n339: - T1、T2、T3 可并行开发\n340: - T4（PublishRuntime 骨架）可在 T1/T2/T3 进行中开始（使用 mock）\n341: - T5（镜像准备流程）需 T1 完成后开始（依赖 DockerService.push_image）\n342: - T6（AgentCube CR 发布）需 T2 完成后开始（依赖 AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime）\n343: - T7（K8s Deployment 发布）需 T3 完成后开始（依赖 KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent）\n344: - T5、T6、T7 可并行开发（在各自依赖完成后）\n345: - T8（元数据更新）仅依赖 T4 的类骨架和 MetadataService（已有），可并行开发\n346: - T9（CLI 命令）需 T4-T8 全部完成后开始\n347: - T10（E2E 集成测试）需 T9 完成后开始\n348: - T11（质量门禁）需所有前置任务完成\n349: \n350: ---\n351: \n352: ## Acceptance Criteria\n353: \n354: | # | Criterion | Command |\n355: |---|-----------|---------|\n356: | AC1 | publish 命令接受所有指定选项 | `kubectl-agentcube publish --help` 显示 13 个选项 |\n357: | AC2 | workspace 默认 `.` | `kubectl-agentcube publish` 使用当前目录 |\n358: | AC3 | provider 默认 `agentcube` | `kubectl-agentcube publish` 使用 agentcube provider |\n359: | AC4 | 未 pack 的工作区报错 | 无 `agent_metadata.yaml` → `ValueError(\"Workspace has not been packaged...\")` |\n360: | AC5 | 无效 provider 报错 | `--provider invalid` → `ValueError` |\n361: | AC6 | 无效 NodePort 报错 | `--node-port 9999` → `ValueError(\"NodePort must be between 30000 and 32767\")` |\n362: | AC7 | local 模式无 image_url 报错 | build_mode=local，无 `--image-url` → `ValueError` |\n363: | AC8 | local 模式 Docker 不可用报错 | Docker 未运行 → `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available...\")` |\n364: | AC9 | agentcube provider 缺少 router_url 报错 | 无 router_url → `ValueError` |\n365: | AC10 | agentcube provider 缺少 workload_manager_url 报错 | 无 workload_manager_url → `ValueError` |\n366: | AC11 | agentcube provider 缺少 readiness probe 报错 | 无 readiness_probe_path/port → `ValueError` |\n367: | AC12 | cloud 模式无 image URL 报错 | build_mode=cloud，无 image URL → `ValueError` |\n368: | AC13 | k8s 部署超时报错 | 120s 未 ready → `RuntimeError` |\n369: | AC14 | 版本号覆盖 | `--version v2.0.0` → metadata.version 更新 |\n370: | AC15 | 描述覆盖 | `--description` → metadata.description 更新 |\n371: | AC16 | 区域覆盖 | `--region cn-north-4` → metadata.region 更新 |\n372: | AC17 | namespace 覆盖 | `--namespace production` → 使用指定 namespace |\n373: | AC18 | replicas 覆盖 | `--replicas 3` → 传递 replicas=3 |\n374: | AC19 | NodePort 覆盖 | `--node-port 30080` → service_url 为 `http://localhost:30080` |\n375: | AC20 | 发布成功更新 metadata | `agent_metadata.yaml` 包含 agent_id, agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment |\n376: | AC21 | agentcube 成功消息 | Rich 格式输出 agent name, agent ID, endpoint |\n377: | AC22 | k8s 成功消息 | Rich 格式输出 deployment name, service name, service URL |\n378: | AC23 | 错误处理：无 verbose | 红色错误消息，无 traceback，exit code 1 |\n379: | AC24 | 错误处理：有 verbose | 红色错误消息 + traceback，exit code 1 |\n380: | AC25 | Progress spinner | 执行期间显示 `\"Publishing agent...\"` spinner |\n381: | AC26 | 覆盖率 ≥ 80% | `pytest --cov=agentcube` |\n382: | AC27 | T/C 比率 > 0.4 | 测试代码行数 / 源代码行数 |\n383: | AC28 | ruff lint 无错误 | `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` |\n384: | AC29 | mypy 类型检查无错误 | `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` |\n385: | AC30 | console script 可用 | `kubectl-agentcube publish --help` 正常输出 |\n\n(End of file - total 385 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** cmd/cli\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** L\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-022/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-022/design.md`, `changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n\n## T1. 扩展 DockerService — 镜像推送支持\n\n- [ ] 1.1 在 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` 中实现 `push_image(self, image_tag: str, registry_url: str, username: Optional[str] = None, password: Optional[str] = None) -> Dict[str, str]`：\n  - 使用 `docker.from_env()` 创建客户端\n  - 调用 `client.images.push(repository, tag, auth_config)` 推送镜像\n  - 返回 `{\"pushed_image\": image_tag, \"status\": \"success\"}`\n- [ ] 1.2 实现 `_docker_login_sdk(self, registry_url: str, username: str, password: str) -> bool`：\n  - 调用 `client.login(username, password, registry_url)`\n  - 成功返回 `True`，失败抛出异常\n- [ ] 1.3 实现 `_tag_image_sdk(self, source_image: str, target_image: str) -> bool`：\n  - 调用 `client.images.get(source_image).tag(target_image)`\n  - 成功返回 `True`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775855460558,"end":1775855460564}}}}
