{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775855483258,"sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","part":{"id":"prt_d793c1d10001H1Rx5RK67qMgyS","messageID":"msg_d793c0da8001uQPeOwVCEfsHtY","sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_b76f17ee3c084ee4a5e1ac62","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli\n**Language:** Python\n**Size:** M\n\n## 目的\n\n为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `invoke` 和 `status` 两个子命令。`invoke` 用于向已部署的 agent 发送请求并获取响应，`status` 用于查询 agent 的运行状态和部署信息。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n\n1. `invoke` Typer 命令实现\n2. `status` Typer 命令实现\n3. `InvokeRuntime` 类实现\n4. `StatusRuntime` 类增强\n\n### 不包含\n\n- `pack` / `build` / `publish` 命令的实现（由 AR-020 / AR-021 / AR-022 覆盖）\n- Go 二进制入口\n- CI/CD pipeline 变更\n\n## 架构概要\n\n```\nCLI Layer (Typer)\n├── invoke() command → InvokeRuntime.invoke()\n└── status() command → StatusRuntime.status()\n\nRuntime Layer\n├── InvokeRuntime — 发送 HTTP 请求到已部署的 agent endpoint\n└── StatusRuntime — 查询 K8s CR 或 Deployment 状态\n```\n\n## 上游依赖\n\n- **AR-022 (`publish` 命令)** — 依赖 publish 部署后的 agent endpoint 和 metadata\n\n## 状态\n\n- [ ] 提案审查\n- [ ] 实现\n- [ ] 验证\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775855483244,"end":1775855483256}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775855492972,"sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","part":{"id":"prt_d793c39f4001QJNDHQOwkR20vm","messageID":"msg_d793c0da8001uQPeOwVCEfsHtY","sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_8367e9ceecfc4394998aa421","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令 — Design\n\n## Overview\n\nThe `invoke` command sends requests to a deployed agent endpoint and displays the response.\nThe `status` command queries the deployment status of an agent from Kubernetes or metadata.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Data Flow\n\n```\ninvoke() CLI → InvokeRuntime.invoke() → HTTP request to agent_endpoint → Rich output\nstatus() CLI → StatusRuntime.status() → K8s API / metadata → Rich status table\n```\n\n### Package Layout\n\n```\ncmd/cli/\n├── agentcube/\n│   ├── cli/\n│   │   └── main.py                    — invoke() and status() commands\n│   ├── runtime/\n│   │   ├── invoke_runtime.py          — InvokeRuntime class\n│   │   └── status_runtime.py          — StatusRuntime class (enhanced)\n│   └── services/\n│       ├── agentcube_provider.py      — get_agent_runtime() for status\n│       └── k8s_provider.py            — get_agent_status() for status\n```\n\n## Component Design\n\n### InvokeRuntime\n\n```python\nclass InvokeRuntime:\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None: ...\n    def invoke(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n```\n\n### StatusRuntime\n\n```python\nclass StatusRuntime:\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None: ...\n    def status(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n    def _get_cr_k8s_status(self, metadata) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n```\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n- Unit tests for InvokeRuntime and StatusRuntime\n- CLI command tests for invoke and status\n- Mock HTTP responses for invoke\n- Mock K8s API for status\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n1. `invoke` loads endpoint from `agent_metadata.yaml` (populated by publish)\n2. `status` checks `k8s_deployment` type to route to correct provider\n3. Both commands use Rich formatting for output\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/design.md","time":{"start":1775855492963,"end":1775855492971}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775855505855,"sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","part":{"id":"prt_d793c6034001ESKyU72OkqzwgA","messageID":"msg_d793c0da8001uQPeOwVCEfsHtY","sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_b56cfa4372b740ad8680fa02","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n- **Language:** Python\n- **Size:** M\n- **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: `invoke` command\n\nThe system SHALL provide an `invoke` subcommand that sends an HTTP request to a deployed agent endpoint.\n\n#### Scenario: Command signature\n- **GIVEN** the CLI is installed\n- **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke --help`\n- **THEN** it SHALL show options for workspace, input/prompt, and verbose\n\n#### Scenario: Invoke with endpoint from metadata\n- **GIVEN** the workspace has been published and `agent_metadata.yaml` contains `agent_endpoint`\n- **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke -f <workspace> --prompt \"hello\"`\n- **THEN** the system SHALL send an HTTP POST request to the endpoint and display the response\n\n#### Scenario: Invoke without published endpoint\n- **GIVEN** the workspace has not been published or `agent_endpoint` is missing\n- **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube invoke`\n- **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating the agent has not been published\n\n### Requirement: `status` command\n\nThe system SHALL provide a `status` subcommand that queries the deployment status of an agent.\n\n#### Scenario: Command signature\n- **GIVEN** the CLI is installed\n- **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube status --help`\n- **THEN** it SHALL show options for workspace and verbose\n\n#### Scenario: Status from AgentRuntime CR\n- **GIVEN** the agent was published with `provider=agentcube`\n- **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube status -f <workspace>`\n- **THEN** the system SHALL query the AgentRuntime CR status and display it\n\n#### Scenario: Status from K8s Deployment\n- **GIVEN** the agent was published with `provider=k8s`\n- **WHEN** the user runs `agentcube status -f <workspace>`\n- **THEN** the system SHALL query the Deployment status and display it\n\n## File changes\n\n| Action | File | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| Modify | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Add `invoke` and `status` Typer commands |\n| Add | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | InvokeRuntime class |\n| Modify | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | Enhance StatusRuntime class |\n| Add | `tests/cli/test_invoke_command.py` | CLI invoke command tests |\n| Add | `tests/cli/test_status_command.py` | CLI status command tests |\n| Add | `tests/runtime/test_invoke_runtime.py` | InvokeRuntime unit tests |\n| Add | `tests/runtime/test_status_runtime.py` | StatusRuntime unit tests |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775855505846,"end":1775855505853}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775855529841,"sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","part":{"id":"prt_d793c9244001qMlXGzoBQkBXqm","messageID":"msg_d793c0da8001uQPeOwVCEfsHtY","sessionID":"ses_286c4542affeXH9FMzi8iYj0mq","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_6f6e2d4b03c34b47b174d5f5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** cmd/cli\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** M\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-023/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-023/design.md`, `changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md`\n> **Dependency:** AR-022 (publish command) — requires published agent endpoint\n\n## T1. 实现 InvokeRuntime 类\n\n- [ ] 1.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`\n- [ ] 1.2 定义 `InvokeRuntime` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n- [ ] 1.3 实现 `invoke(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n  - 加载 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n  - 校验 `agent_endpoint` 存在 → 否则 `ValueError`\n  - 发送 HTTP POST 请求到 endpoint\n  - 返回响应结果\n- [ ] 1.4 创建对应测试文件\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_invoke_runtime.py -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T2. 增强 StatusRuntime 类\n\n- [ ] 2.1 修改 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`\n- [ ] 2.2 实现 `status(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n  - 加载 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n  - 根据 `k8s_deployment.type` 路由到正确的状态查询\n  - 返回状态信息\n- [ ] 2.3 实现/增强 `_get_cr_k8s_status(self, metadata) -> Dict[str, Any]`\n- [ ] 2.4 创建对应测试文件\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_status_runtime.py -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T3. 实现 CLI invoke 命令入口\n\n- [ ] 3.1 在 `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` 中添加 `invoke` 命令\n- [ ] 3.2 选项：`workspace`, `prompt`, `verbose`\n- [ ] 3.3 命令体：调用 `InvokeRuntime.invoke()`，Rich 格式输出响应\n- [ ] 3.4 创建对应测试文件\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_invoke_command.py -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T4. 实现 CLI status 命令入口\n\n- [ ] 4.1 在 `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` 中添加 `status` 命令\n- [ ] 4.2 选项：`workspace`, `verbose`\n- [ ] 4.3 命令体：调用 `StatusRuntime.status()`，Rich Table 格式输出状态\n- [ ] 4.4 创建对应测试文件\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_status_command.py -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T5. 代码质量门禁与最终验证\n\n- [ ] 5.1 运行 `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认无 lint 错误\n- [ ] 5.2 运行 `ruff format --check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认格式合规\n- [ ] 5.3 运行 `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认无类型错误\n- [ ] 5.4 运行 `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v --cov=agentcube` 确认覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n- [ ] 5.5 运行 `kubectl-agentcube invoke --help` 确认帮助输出\n- [ ] 5.6 运行 `kubectl-agentcube status --help` 确认帮助输出\n\n**Verification:** 以上全部通过；exit code 均为 0\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1 (InvokeRuntime) ───────────────────────────────┐\n                                                   │\nT2 (StatusRuntime) ────────────────────────────────┤\n                                                   │\nT3 (CLI invoke 命令) ←── T1 ───────────────────────┤\n                                                   │\nT4 (CLI status 命令) ←── T2 ───────────────────────┤\n                                                   │\nT5 (质量门禁) ←── T3, T4 ──────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Parallel execution:**\n- T1 和 T2 可并行开发\n- T3 需 T1 完成后开始\n- T4 需 T2 完成后开始\n- T3 和 T4 可并行开发\n- T5 需所有前置任务完成\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n| # | Criterion | Command |\n|---|-----------|---------|\n| AC1 | invoke 命令接受 workspace 和 prompt 选项 | `kubectl-agentcube invoke --help` |\n| AC2 | status 命令接受 workspace 选项 | `kubectl-agentcube status --help` |\n| AC3 | 未发布的 agent invoke 报错 | 无 `agent_endpoint` → `ValueError` |\n| AC4 | invoke 发送 HTTP 请求并显示响应 | Rich 格式输出 |\n| AC5 | status 查询并显示部署状态 | Rich Table 格式 |\n| AC6 | 覆盖率 ≥ 80% | `pytest --cov=agentcube` |\n| AC7 | ruff lint 无错误 | `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` |\n| AC8 | mypy 类型检查无错误 | `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnost